rat-kohli-hardik-pandya-practice-despite-not-playing-against-bangladesh-in-asia-cup-2023-watch-4394393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20were%20both%20seen%20getting%20ready%20for%20practice%20despite%20not%20playing%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20Asia%20Cup%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fno-time-for-rest-virat-kohli-hardik-pandya-practice-despite-not-playing-against-bangladesh-in-asia-cup-2023-watch-4394393%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fno-time-for-rest-virat-kohli-hardik-pandya-practice-despite-not-playing-against-bangladesh-in-asia-cup-2023-watch-4394393%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fno-time-for-rest-virat-kohli-hardik-pandya-practice-despite-not-playing-against-bangladesh-in-asia-cup-2023-watch-4394393%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20India%2C%20Canada%20Halt%20Trade%20Deal%20Amid%20Strain.%20Where%20Are%20Ties%20Headed%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20setback%20to%20already%20complicated%20relations%2C%20Canada's%20trade%20commission%20announced%20on%20its%20website%20that%20the%20trade%20mission%20to%20India%20had%20been%20postponed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mission%20was%20tied%20up%20with%20Canada's%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%20and%20India%20was%20described%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bideal%20destination%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20Team%20Canada%20Trade%20Mission.%20%26quot%3BCanada%20and%20India%20have%20a%20mutual%20interest%20in%20expanding%20our%20commercial%20relationship%20and%20growing%20people-to-people%20connections%2C%26quot%3B%20Canada%20had%20said.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20trade%20deal%20negotiations%20were%20also%20halted%20last%20month%20by%20Ottawa%20and%20no%20specifics%20were%20put%20forward.%20Before%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20was%20heading%20to%20India%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20in%20Singapore%20about%20the%20reason%20for%20pausing%20the%20trade%20negotiations.%20He%20cautiously%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20the%20negotiations%20around%20free%20trade%20are%20long%20and%20complex%20and%20I%20won't%20say%20any%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20reported%20by%20Canadian%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Canada%20had%20first%20launched%20negotiations%20for%20a%20trade%20deal%2013%20years%20ago%20in%202010.%20After%20a%20lull%20of%20almost%205%20years%2C%20the%20talks%20restarted%20in%202022%20with%20renegotiations%20on%20a%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement.%20Within%20a%20year%2C%20the%20talks%20seem%20to%20have%20once%20again%20hit%20a%20rough%20patch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20Delhi%20last%20week%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20the%20chill%20in%20the%20relationship%20was%20visible.%20India%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20conveyed%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20concerns%20about%20continuing%20anti-India%20activities%20of%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Canada%26quot%3B.%20The%20statement%20added%20that%20the%20anti-India%20activists%20were%20%26quot%3Bpromoting%20secessionism%20and%20inciting%20violence%20against%20Indian%20diplomats%2C%20damaging%20diplomatic%20premises%2C%20and%20threatening%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Canada%20and%20their%20places%20of%20worship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20meeting%2C%20PM%20Trudeau%20pointed%20indirectly%20to%20India%20for%20interference%20in%20its%20internal%20matters.%20He%20told%20the%20media%20that%20%26quot%3Bdiaspora%20Canadians%20make%20up%20a%20huge%20proportion%20of%20our%20country%20and%20they%20should%20be%20able%20to%20express%20themselves%20and%20make%20their%20choices%20without%20interference%20from%20any%20of%20the%20many%20countries%20that%20we%20know%20are%20involved%20in%20interference%20challenges%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%20a%20group%20banned%20in%20India%2C%20held%20a%20Khalistan%20%26quot%3Breferendum%26quot%3B%20in%20Surrey%20in%20British%20Columbia%20as%20Day%202%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20took%20place%20in%20India%20on%20September%2010.%20India%20has%20raised%20objections%20to%20such%20activities%20in%20the%20past%20with%20not%20just%20Canada%20but%20even%20UK%20and%20Australia%2C%20saying%20this%20is%20a%20secessionist%20call%20that%20threatens%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20India%20and%20shouldn't%20be%20allowed%20by%20countries%20that%20respect%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrudeau's%20support%20for%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20in%20India%20in%202020%20had%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%20New%20Delhi%20had%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%20interference%26quot%3B%20in%20India's%20affairs.%20The%20then%20Canadian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20India%2C%20Nadir%20Patel%2C%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20and%20handed%20a%20demarche%2C%20or%20a%20diplomatic%20note.%20The%20statement%20from%20India%20had%20also%20warned%20that%20it%20could%20have%20serious%20damaging%20impact%20on%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20home%20in%20Canada%2C%20Trudeau%20has%20faced%20some%20bad%20press%20over%20what%20has%20been%20called%20by%20a%20CTV%20contributor%20Don%20Martin%20as%20the%20second%20Delhi%20debacle.%20After%20the%20strained%20exchange%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20G20%2C%20the%20Canadian%20PM%20was%20unable%20to%20fly%20back%20home%20for%20two%20days%20as%20his%20plane%20developed%20a%20snag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20is%20already%20confronting%20sagging%20popularity%20ratings%20over%20affordability%20concerns%20in%20Canada%20and%20tough%20questions%20from%20the%20opposition%20over%20a%20housing%20crisis%20and%20food%20inflation.%20For%20the%20moment%2C%20he%20has%20ruled%20out%20stepping%20down%20saying%20he%20will%20tackle%20the%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20trade%20negotiations%20restarted%20in%202022%20after%20a%20pause%2C%20many%20were%20hopeful%20that%20the%20relationship%20would%20slowly%20be%20brought%20back%20from%20the%20edge%2C%20even%20if%20transactionally.%20However%2C%20the%20diplomatic%20fallout%20over%20issues%20ranging%20from%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20Khalistan%20to%20allegations%20of%20political%20interference%20have%20impacted%20trade%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Maha%20Siddiqui%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20extensively%20reported%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20global%20affairs.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694840040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ffneil63o_pm-modi-justin-trudeau-_625x300_11_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fanalysis-new-snag-raises-questions-over-future-of-india-canada-ties-4394700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20latest%20setback%20to%20already%20complicated%20relations%2C%20Canada's%20trade%20commission%20announced%20on%20its%20website%20that%20the%20trade%20mission%20to%20India%20had%20been%20postponed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fanalysis-new-snag-raises-questions-over-future-of-india-canada-ties-4394700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fanalysis-new-snag-raises-questions-over-future-of-india-canada-ties-4394700%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fanalysis-new-snag-raises-questions-over-future-of-india-canada-ties-4394700%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20One%20Terrorist%20Killed%20in%20Encounter%20Near%20LoC%E2%80%99s%20Baramulla%22%2C%22cont