%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20criticism%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20High%20Court%2C%20sharing%20how%20the%20process%20is%20being%20made%20transparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Collegium%2C%20which%20is%20tasked%20which%20the%20appointments%2C%20has%20prepared%20a%20broad%20platform%20where%20it%20has%20assessed%2050%20judges%20for%20consideration%20for%20elevation%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20he%20said%20while%20delivering%20the%20Ram%20Jethmalani%20Memorial%20Lecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20turned%20down%20claims%20that%20the%20Collegium%20has%20no%20factual%20data%20to%20evaluate%20the%20candidates%20and%20said%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3BCentre%20for%20Research%20and%20Planning%26quot%3B%2C%20headed%20by%20an%20officer%20from%20the%20Haryana%20judicial%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20prepared%20a%20broad%20platform%20where%20we%20have%20assessed%20the%20top%2050%20judges%20of%20the%20country%20who%20would%20be%20considered%20for%20appointment%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20We%20have%20data%20on%20judgements%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20judgements.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20make%20the%20process%20of%20appointment%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20more%20transparent%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20lay%20down%20objective%20parameters%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20National%20Judicial%20Data%20Grid%20for%20helping%20it%20with%20real-time%20tracking%20of%20case%20disposal%20and%20pendency%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20information%20will%20help%20the%20Court%20identify%20the%20areas%20of%20concern%20to%20decrease%20pendency.%20Institutionalisation%20requires%20policy%20solutions.%20Due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20data%2C%20it%20has%20been%20painfully%20difficult%20to%20devise%20methods%20to%20reduce%20pendency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20as%20per%20NJDG%20data%2C%20there%20are%2062946%20pending%20civil%20cases%20and%2017555%20pending%20criminal%20cases.%20We%20have%20had%20a%20disposal%20rate%20of%2095.34%20per%20cent%20this%20year.%20This%20data%20will%20help%20me%20prioritise%20certain%20categories%20of%20matters%20(such%20as%20the%20oldest%20pending%20cases)%20for%20their%20able%20disposal%20and%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20introspect%20our%20performance%20in%20terms%20of%20disposal%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694838720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4s1m01fo_cji-dy-chandrachud-ani_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-on-how-judges-appointment-process-is-being-made-transparent-4394784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20criticism%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20High%20Court%2C%20sharing%20how%20the%20process%20is%20being%20made%20transparent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-on-how-judges-appointment-process-is-being-made-transparent-4394784%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-on-how-judges-appointment-process-is-being-made-transparent-4394784%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-on-how-judges-appointment-process-is-being-made-transparent-4394784%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunil%20Grover%3A%20I%20will%20never%20get%20bored%20of%20wearing%20sari%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694838600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103691875%2Cimgsize-64916