%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chaos%20At%20NIT%20Silchar%20As%20Students%20Clash%20With%20Police%20After%20Suicide%20On%20Campus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStudents%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20at%20Silchar%20in%20Cachar%20district%20of%20Assam%20on%20Friday%20night%20clashed%20with%20the%20police%20during%20an%20aggressive%20protest%20after%20the%20death%20of%20one%20of%20their%20fellow%20students%20at%20the%20college%20hostel.%20A%20student%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20third%20semester%20of%20the%20electric%20engineering%20course%2C%20allegedly%20hung%20himself%20after%20he%20failed%20exams%20and%20couldn't%20clear%20his%20back%20papers%2C%20sources%20said.%20He%20had%20requested%20the%20college%20authorities%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20register%20for%20the%20next%20semester%2C%20but%20it%20was%20reportedly%20turned%20down%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20they%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20mild%20use%20of%20force%20to%20disperse%20the%20agitating%20students%20after%20tensions%20in%20the%20campus%20escalated%20as%20the%20students%20surrounded%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20Registrar.%20A%20case%20of%20unnatural%20death%20has%20been%20registered%2C%20and%20the%20police%20have%20recovered%20the%20dead%20body%20and%20sent%20it%20for%20post-mortem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20under%20control%20now%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20police%20said%2C%20but%20tension%20prevails%20as%20more%20student%20agitation%20is%20expected%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cachar%20district%20authorities%2C%20police%2C%20and%20the%20authorities%20of%20NIT%20Silchar%20had%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20over%20the%20prevailing%20situation%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20premier%20institute%20might%20remain%20closed%20until%20the%20situation%20is%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agitating%20students%20are%20upset%20at%20some%20new%20guidelines%20introduced%20by%20the%20college%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20we%20waited%20the%20whole%20night%20for%20NIT%20Silchar%20Director%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20meet%20with%20us%20and%20declined%20all%20our%20requests.%20Every%20day%2C%20the%20institution%20has%20been%20introducing%20new%20guidelines%20for%20students.%20The%20students%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20administration%20of%20NIT%20Silchar.%20Today%2C%20one%20of%20the%20students%20died%20by%20suicide%20due%20to%20depression%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20agitating%20students%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20allege%20they%20were%20protesting%20peacefully%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20meet%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20institute%2C%20but%20were%20met%20with%20police%20batons%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20student%2C%20our%20senior%2C%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20and%20we%20were%20doing%20peaceful%20agitation%20but%20the%20authorities%20of%20NIT%20Silchar%20didn't%20even%20bother%20to%20come%20and%20talk%20to%20us.%20They%20unleashed%20police%20on%20us%2C%20police%20lathi-charged%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20protesting%20student%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20college%20administration%20confirmed%20the%20suicide%2C%20saying%20there%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bproblems%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20student%20since%20his%20first%20year%20itself%2C%20and%20he%20might%20have%20been%20depressed%20as%20he%20couldn't%20clear%20backlogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20happened%2C%20and%20we%20are%20all%20very%20sad%20about%20it.%20We%20responded%20promptly.%20There%20are%20some%20allegations%2C%20which%20are%20on%20a%20case-to-case%20basis%2C%20there%20were%20some%20small%20incidents%20before%2C%20but%20with%20this%20student%2C%20I%20am%20told%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20first%20year%20there%20were%20problems%2C%20there%20were%20some%20backlogs%20and%20because%20of%20these%20backlogs%20he%20could%20not%20move%20with%20his%20batch%20and%20that%20might%20have%20created%20depression%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20Dilip%20Kumar%20Baidya%2C%20Director%2C%20NIT%20Silchar%2C%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20administration%20is%20always%20ready%2C%20but%20his%20friends%20should%20have%20noticed%20the%20student's%20mental%20state%20and%20flagged%20it%20to%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20students%20vandalised%20cars%20and%20ransacked%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20Dean%2C%20and%20they%20had%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20de-escalate%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20information%20about%20the%20suicide%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20we%20rushed%20here.%20The%20behaviour%20of%20the%20students%20was%20a%20bit%20unruly%2C%20they%20vandalised%20a%20few%20cars%2C%20and%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20dean%20was%20completely%20ransacked.%20We%20tried%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20student%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours.%20NIT%20will%20form%20an%20enquiry%20committee.%20The%20students%20were%20highly%20agitated%2C%20they%20resorted%20to%20violence%20and%20even%20as%20we%20were%20negotiating%20with%20them%2C%20they%20suddenly%20started%20throwing%20water%20bottles%20at%20us.%20We%20have%20decided%20that%20if%20the%20situation%20does%20not%20improve%2C%20we%20have%20to%20take%20some%20steps%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Cachar%2C%20Rohan%20Kumar%20Jha%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%