%20enforcement%20officials%20began%20investigating%20claims%20of%20theft%20occurring%20at%20the%20checkpoint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20theft%20has%20emerged%20now%2C%20showing%20the%20agents%20working%20together%20to%20take%20money%20from%20wallets%20and%20purses%20that%20passed%20them%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20X-ray%20machine.%20In%20the%20footage%2C%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20is%20seen%20putting%20his%20hand%20inside%20a%20wallet%20and%20slipping%20the%20money%20inside%20his%20own%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETSA%20Agents%20caught%20on%20surveillance%20video%20stealing%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20in%20cash%20from%20passengers'%20bags%20at%20Miami%20airport.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLhFW9yNRNV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLhFW9yNRNV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mike%20Sington%20(%40MikeSington)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMikeSington%2Fstatus%2F1702102526731202655%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20per%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Ffox-news-crime%2Fsurveillance-footage-catches-tsa-agents-stealing-from-passengers-miami-international%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Fox%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20duo%20along%20with%20Elizabeth%20Fuster%20were%20arrested%20in%20July%20and%20initially%20charged%20with%20organized%20scheme%20to%20defraud%2C%20according%20to%20Miami-Dade%20County%20jail%20records.%20They%20were%20booked%20into%20Turner%20Guilford%20Knight%20Detention%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuster%20and%20Gonzalez%20confessed%20to%20''numerous%20thefts''%20from%20travelers%2C%20admitting%20to%20stealing%20an%20average%20of%20%241%2C000%20daily%20while%20working%20together.%20Both%20of%20them%20have%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20third-degree%20felony%20grand%20theft%20charges%20they%20face%2C%20while%C2%A0charges%20against%20Fuster%20were%20dropped%20in%20August.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20officers%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20screening%20duties%20pending%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20investigation%20and%20administrative%20actions%2C%20according%20to%20the%20TSA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20by%20TSA%20stated%2C%20''The%20Transportation%20Security%20Administration%20holds%20its%20Transportation%20Security%20Officers%20(TSOs)%20to%20the%20highest%20professional%20and%20ethical%20standards%20and%20has%20no%20tolerance%20for%20misconduct%20in%20the%20workplace.''%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''We%20actively%20and%20aggressively%20investigated%20these%20misconduct%20allegations%20and%20presented%20our%20findings%20to%20the%20Miami%20Dade%20Police%20Department%2C%20and%20are%20working%20closely%20with%20them.%20Any%20employee%20who%20fails%20to%20meet%20our%20fundamental%20ethical%20standards%20is%20held%20accountable%2C''%20the%20statement%20added.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694833140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fut22s1v_us-airport-officers-caught-stealing-money_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-airport-officers-caught-on-camera-stealing-money-from-passengers-bags-4394652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20officers%20allegedly%20stole%20at%20least%20%24600%20in%20cash%20and%20other%20items%20from%20passengers'%20luggage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-airport-officers-caught-on-camera-stealing-money-from-passengers-bags-4394652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-airport-officers-caught-on-camera-stealing-money-from-passengers-bags-4394652%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-airport-officers-caught-on-camera-stealing-money-from-passengers-bags-4394652%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nipah%20Mortality%20Rate%20Upto%2070%25%2C%20Compared%20To%20Covid's%203%25%3A%20Top%20Medical%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20mortality%20rate%20among%20those%20infected%20with%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20is%20much%20higher%20compared%20to%20those%20infected%20with%20Covid%2C%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20chief%20Dr%20Rajiv%20Bahl%20said%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dr%20Bahl%2C%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20has%20a%20mortality%20rate%20between%2040-70%20per%20cent%20compared%20to%20Covid's%202-3%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20case%20of%20Nipah%20virus%20was%20confirmed%20in%20Kerala's%20Kozhikode%20yesterday%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20people%20infected%20in%20the%20state%20to%20six.%20Two%20of%20the%20earlier%20cases%20have%20been%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20rise%20in%20cases%20in%20Kerala%2C%20India%20has%20called%20on%20Australia%20to%20supply%2020%20more%20doses%20of%20monoclonal%20antibody%20to%20treat%20Nipah%20virus%20infections%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICMR%2C%20in%20light%20of%20the%20recurring%20Nipah%20virus%20outbreaks%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20and%20its%20high%20mortality%20rate%20compared%20to%20Covid%2C%20said%20it%20is%20planning%20to%20start%20work%20on%20developing%20a%20vaccine%20against%20the%20viral%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20some%20doses%20of%20monoclonal%20antibody%20from%20Australia%20in%202018.%20Currently%2C%20the%20doses%20are%20available%20for%20only%2010%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20DrBahl%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr%20Bahl%20said%2014%20people%20who%20contracted%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20outside%20of%20India%20have%20made%20a%20full%20recovery%20after%20receiving%20monoclonal%20antibody%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20phase%201%20trial%20to%20establish%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20medicine%20has%20been%20done%20outside.%20Efficacy%20trials%20have%20not%20been%20done.%20It%20can%20only%20given%20as%20compassionate%20use%20medicine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20rising%20cases%2C%20all%20educational%20institutions%20in%20Kozhikode%20will%20be%20closed%20for%20a%20week%20starting%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKerala%20health%20minister%20Veena%20George%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20contact%20list%20of%20Nipah%20virus%20patients%20in%20Kerala%20has%20grown%20to%201%2C080.%20Of%20these%2C%20327%20are%20healthcare%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694832840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4ckdn2vo_kerala-nipah_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-mortality-rate-higher-than-covid-top-medical-body-4394640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mortality%20rate%20among%20those%20infected%20with%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20is%20much%20higher%20compared%20to%20those%20infected%20with%20Covid%2C%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20chief%20Dr%20Rajiv%20Bahl%20said%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-mortality-rate-higher-than-covid-top-medical-body-4394640%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-mortality-rate-higher-than-covid-top-medical-body-4394640%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-mortality-rate-higher-than-covid-top-medical-body-4394640%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Hyd%20to%20meet%20friends%2C%20Maoist%20leader%20with%20Rs%2025L%20bounty%20in%20cop%20net%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694832781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1037