pected%20After%203%20Days%20Of%20Raids%20Against%20Azam%20Khan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20Income%20Tax%20department%20suspected%20a%20tax%20evasion%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%20800%20crore%20by%20senior%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Azam%20Khan%20after%20it%20conducted%20raids%20on%20him%20and%20people%20associated%20with%20him%20for%20three%20days%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncome%20tax%20sleuths%20who%20reached%20Khan's%20residence%20on%20Jail%20Road%20in%20Rampur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20at%207%20am%20on%20Wednesday%20completed%20their%20search%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20officials%20left%20his%20residence%20around%207%20pm%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20came%20out%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20raid%20of%20I-T%20department.%20They%20stayed%20here%20for%20three%20days.%20They%20conducted%20searches%20and%20asked%20questions.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khan%20refused%20to%20answer%20further%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2013%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20conducted%20raids%20at%20more%20than%2030%20premises%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20as%20part%20of%20a%20tax%20evasion%20probe%20against%20Mr%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20said%20the%20department%20has%20conducted%20raids%20in%20Rampur%2C%20Saharanpur%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Ghaziabad%20and%20Meerut%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20apart%20from%20some%20premises%20in%20neighbouring%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Ghaziabad%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20raided%20a%20residence%20in%20Rajnagar%20Colony%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20house%20belongs%20to%20Ekta%20Kaushik%2C%20said%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Azam%20Khan's%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20I-T%20probe%20is%20related%20to%20some%20trusts%20run%20by%20Khan%20and%20his%20family%20members%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scope%20of%20investigation%20by%20the%20I-T%20department%20intensified%20with%20sleuths%20reaching%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20and%20district%20panchayat%20office%20besides%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jauhar%20University%20headed%20by%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20the%20government%20expenditure%20files%20are%20being%20scrutinized%20as%20over%20Rs%20800%20crore%20tax%20evasion%20was%20suspected%20by%20the%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20drew%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20which%20vowed%20support%20to%20Khan%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Bdictatorship%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisusing%20central%20agencies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAzam%20Khan%20saheb%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20truth.%20He%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20better%20future%20for%20children%20and%20built%20a%20university%20for%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20in%20Hindi%20following%20the%20raids%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKhan%20has%20always%20fought%20against%20communal%20forces.%20We%20all%20stand%20united%20with%20his%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20allegations%20about%20misuse%20of%20central%20agencies%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20had%20said%20the%20central%20agencies%20were%20well%20within%20their%20rights%20to%20take%20action%20to%20make%20%26quot%3BBharat%20corruption-free%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20court%20had%20convicted%20Khan%20in%20a%20hate%20speech%20case%20registered%20over%20his%20remark%20made%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Khatanagaria%20village%20of%20the%20Milak%20Kotwali%20area%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20sentenced%20to%20three%20years%20of%20imprisonment%2C%20following%20which%20he%20was%20disqualified%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20Rampur.%20Later%2C%20he%20was%20acquitted%20by%20a%20higher%20court%2C%20but%20his%20disqualification%20was%20not%20revoked%20on%20account%20of%20his%20convic