s%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdisney-world-epcot-attractions-ranking-2022-5%5C%22%3Evisits%20to%20Epcot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20usually%20with%20a%20cocktail%20in%20hand%20as%20she%20strolls%20through%20the%20world%20showcase%20with%20its%20pavilions%20modeled%20after%20countries%20from%20Italy%20to%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachul's%20parents%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Disney%20Vacation%20Club%2C%20a%20timeshare%20program%2C%20accompany%20her%20on%20some%20visits%2C%20helping%20make%20the%20trips%20more%20affordable%20than%2C%20say%2C%20a%20vacation%20to%20Tuscany.%20When%20she%20turns%2030%20next%20year%2C%20Rachul%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20are%20already%20set%20to%20ring%20in%20her%20third%20decade%20aboard%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhy-im-taking-another-disney-cruise-2023-7%5C%22%3EDisney%20cruise%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachul%20is%20one%20of%20a%20growing%20share%20of%2020-%20and%2030-somethings%20without%20kids%20who%20are%20packing%20into%20Disney%20parks%2C%20particularly%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Orlando%20%E2%80%94%20frequently%20making%20these%20often-lavish%20trips%20as%20couples%20or%20in%20groups%20of%20friends.%20That's%20according%20to%20interviews%20Insider%20conducted%20with%20more%20than%2020%20people%2C%20ranging%20from%20annual%20pass%20holders%20to%20current%20and%20former%20Disney%20employees%20(most%20of%20whom%20requested%20anonymity%20to%20speak%20freely%20about%20company%20business%20and%20policies)%20to%20travel%20agents%20and%20others%20familiar%20with%20foot%20traffic%20at%20the%20parks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollectively%2C%20they%20painted%20a%20picture%20of%20an%20undeniable%20demographic%20shift%20that%20could%20have%20big%20implications%20for%20Disney's%20parks'%20business%2C%20from%20an%20influx%20of%20consumer%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20childless%20earners%20tend%20to%20have%20more%20disposable%20income%20than%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20to%20an%20impact%20on%20in-park%20rides%20and%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phenomenon%20is%20beginning%20to%20lay%20waste%20to%20the%20stigma%20surrounding%20the%20%26quot%3BDisney%20adult%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20term%20that%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbeing-a-disney-adult-what-its-like-essay-2022-9%5C%22%3Eused%20to%20poke%20fun%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20grown-ups%20with%20a%20tendency%20to%20display%20their%20die-hard%20devotion%20to%20the%20Mouse%20House.%20One%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urbandictionary.com%2Fdefine.php%3Fterm%3DDisney%2520Adult%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUrban%20Dictionary%20entry%3C%2Fa%3E%20defined%20a%20%26quot%3BDisney%20adult%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20millennial%20who%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20stop%20talking%20about%20Disney%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20terrifyingly%20intense%20people%20you'll%20ever%20encounter.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20idea%20of%20donning%20a%20pair%20of%20Mickey%20ears%20or%20%26quot%3BDisneyBounding%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20dressing%20for%20park%20visits%20in%20outfits%20inspired%20by%20famous%20Disney%20characters%20%E2%80%94%20is%20becoming%20more%20mainstream%2C%20and%20perhaps%20even%20cool%2C%20for%20more%20and%20more%20kidless%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers.%20Disney's%20not%20just%20for%20hot%2C%20tired%20parents%20chaperoning%20their%20kids%20from%20character%20breakfasts%20to%20rides%20on%20Aladdin's%20magic%20carpets%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20two%20hours%20away%2C%20but%20it's%20an%20escape%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Molly%20May%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20mental-health%20counselor%20based%20in%20Florida%2C%20who%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20has%20held%20an%20annual%20Disney%20World%20pass%20for%20several%20years.%20The%20couple%20got%20engaged%20there%2C%20celebrated%20their%20five-year%20anniversary%20at%20Disneyland%2C%20and%20visited%20Disneyland%20Paris%20earlier%20this%20year.%20They're%20planning%20to%20comm