0over%20the%20age%20of%2021%20who%20get%20tipsy%20shuffling%20from%20one%20country%20pavilion%20to%20the%20next%2C%20ordering%20internationally%20inspired%20cocktails%20or%20sipping%20flights%20of%20spirits%20at%20venues%20like%20the%20Mexico%20pavilion's%20La%20Cava%20del%20Tequila%20bar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20that%20dining%20glow-up%2C%20multiple%20high-tech%20rides%20have%20debuted%20since%20last%20year%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20fresh%20slate%20of%20holiday%20experiences%20lined%20up%20for%20this%20winter.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20Disney%20is%20pushing%20to%20be%20competitive%20for%20that%20adult%2C%20thrill-seeking%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20de%20Araujo%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Disney-authorized%20travel-planning%20service%20The%20Vacationeer%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Disney%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story%2C%20and%20company%20insiders%20say%20obtaining%20data%20about%20any%20aspect%20of%20the%20business%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20foot%20traffic%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20opaque%20(the%20Journal's%20reporting%2C%20for%20example%2C%20was%20based%20on%20stats%20from%20the%20third-party%20company%20Touring%20Plans%2C%20which%20tracks%20wait%20times%20for%20rides).%20But%2C%20according%20to%20a%20former%20Disney%20executive%20with%20close%20knowledge%20of%20Disney%20World%2C%20between%2040%25%20to%2050%25%20of%20typical%20crowds%20at%20the%20Orlando%20parks%20are%20composed%20of%20adults%20visiting%20without%20children%20%E2%80%94%20people%20the%20executive%20categorized%20as%20%26quot%3Bnonfamily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20number%20is%20%26quot%3Bastonishing%20when%20you%20think%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20executive%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20travel%20marketing%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20it's%20not%20the%20perception%20that%20people%20have.%26quot%3B%20And%20that%20stat%20has%20been%20on%20a%20gradual%20uptick%20for%20several%20years%2C%20this%20person%20and%20others%20familiar%20with%20Disney%20World's%20foot%20traffic%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETara%20Goldstein%20and%20Ann%20van%20Oostendorp%2C%20independent%20travel%20planners%20who%20specialize%20in%20Disney%20trips%20and%20call%20themselves%20the%20%26quot%3BMagic%20Planning%20Sisters%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Insider%20that%20between%20mid-2020%20and%202023%2C%2053%25%20of%20the%20Disney%20vacations%20they%20planned%20were%20for%20adults%20only.%20They%20attributed%20much%20of%20the%20shift%20to%20the%20advent%20of%20hot%20rides%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20cutting-edge%20roller%20coaster%20themed%20after%20the%20tentpole%20%26quot%3BGuardians%20of%20the%20Galaxy%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20that%20appeal%20to%20an%20older%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisney%20knows%20the%20kids%20want%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20van%20Oostendorp%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20it's%20time%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20adult%20population.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20weddings%20to%20special%20meals%2C%20millennials%20without%20kids%20are%20bringing%20disposable%20income%20to%20the%20parks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-three-year-old%20Natalie%20Schwartz%20remembers%20all%20the%20visits%20she%20and%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20Brett%2C%20made%20to%20Disney%20World%20as%20students%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tampa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20always%20have%20had%20this%20little-girl%20dream%20of%20getting%20married%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwartz%20told%20Insider%20several%20weeks%20after%20her%20June%20wedding%2C%20a%20nearly%20120-person%20affair%20at%20Disney%20World's%20Grand%20Floridian%20resort.%20Among%20the%20perks%20were%20discounted%20park%20tickets%20the%20couple%20could%20share%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20friends%2C%20and%20together%20they%20spent%20two%20days%20venturing%20through%20the%20parks%20ahead%20of%20the%20ceremony.%20Schwartz%20also%20took%20her%20grandmother%20on%20the%20It's%20a%20Small%20World%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20summer%2C%20Schwartz%20returned%20to%20Disney%20World%20to%20celebrate%20her%20friend%20Sierra%20Keller's%2024th%20birthday.%20%26quot%3BDisney%20kind%20of%20just%20transports%20us%20somewhere%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Keller%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20about%2010%20minutes%20from%20the%20parks%20in%20a%20home%20her%20family%20built%20specifically%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Disney.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20worried%20about%20elections.%20You're%20not%20worried%20about%20laws%20passing%20or%20what%20tomorrow's%20going%20to%20look%20like%2C%20or%20how%20many%20bills%20do%20I%20need%20to%20pay%20or%20anything.%20You're%20just%20in%20that%20moment%20and%20you%20get%20to%20kind%20of%20be%20carefree.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%20World%20Wedding%20of%20Natalie%20and%20Brett%20Schwartz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650226291afe8f0019e9facc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENewlyweds%20Natalie%20and%20Brett%20Schwartz%20exchanged%20vows%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Orlando%20this%20summer.%3Cp%3EDisney%20Fine%20Art%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20share%20of%20visitors%20like%20Schwartz%20and%20Keller%20has%20%26quot%3Bslowly%20influenced%20the%20product%20choices%26quot%3B%20within%20the%20parks%2C%20the%20former%20Disney%20travel%20marketing%20executive%20said.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20groups%20bringing%20new%20spending%20are%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20drive%20those%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20executive%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20it%20and%20you%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20baby%20rides%2C'%20it's%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20wait%20a%20minute%20%E2%80%94%20do%20we%20really%20need%20those%3F%20Don't%20we%20have%20that%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Epcot%20added%20Space%20220%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdinner-at-space-220-is-it-worth-it-photos-disney-world-2023%5C%22%3Eupscale%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20for%20the%20Instagram%20age.%20The%20decor%20could%20only%20be%20described%20as%20interstellar%20chic%20%E2%80%94%20think%20big%20bay%20windows%20overlooking%20a%20simulated%20image%20of%20the%20Earth.%20Jason%20Petrina%2C%20the%20restaurant's%20general%20manager%2C%20told%20Insider%20he's%20seen%20more%20adults%20without%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20couples%2C%20friend%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20coming%20in%20lately%2C%20noting%20that%20many%20are%20local%20annual%20pass%20holders%20or%20members%20of%20Disney's%20timeshare%20program.%20He's%20gotten%20to%20know%20some%20regulars%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20really%20concerned%20about%20spending%20money%20as%20long%20as%20they%20get%20a%20great%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Petrina%20said.%20And%20that%20could%20mean%20springing%20for%20premium%20wines%20or%20lavish%20dishes%20like%20rib-eye%20steaks%20or%20lobster.%20He%20estimated%20that%2015%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20the%20restaurant's%20income%20stems%20from%20this%20group%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20piece%20of%20our%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20down%2015%20to%2020%25%20in%20sales%2C%20you%20might%20close.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrinking%20with%20mates%20or%20boozing%20with%20Mickey%3F%20How%20Disney's%20parks%20and%20retail%20experience%20is%20evolving.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20parks%2C%20signs%20of%20Disney's%20efforts%20to%20satisfy%20an%20older%20crowd%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20group%20it%20has%20lured%20to%20cineplexes%20with%20its%20investments%20in%20the%20Star%20Wars%20and%20Marvel%20franchises%20%E2%80%94%20seem%20ubiquitous.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20obvious%20examples%20is%20the%20Guardians%20of%20the%20Galaxy%3A%20Cosmic%20Rewind%20roller%20coaster%2C%20which%20opened%20in%20May%202022%20and%20features%20preshow%20content%20starring%20actors%20like%20Chris%20Evans%20and%20Zoe%20Salda%C3%B1a.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coaster%20%E2%80%94%20which%20launches%20riders%20backward%20before%20hurtling%20them%20into%20a%20dark%2C%20cavernous%20space%20meant%20to%20emulate%20the%20universe%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20features%20songs%20like%20%26quot%3BSeptember%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20Wants%20to%20Rule%20the%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20hits%20likelier%20to%20perk%20up%20older%20ears%20than%20younger%20ones.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20Magic%20Kingdom%20added%20Tron%3A%20Lightcycle%20Run%2C%20an%20indoor-outdoor%20coaster%20with%20motorcycle-like%20seating.%20Both%20rides%20offer%20a%20far%20more%20thrill-seeking%20edge%20than%20stalwarts%20like%20It's%20a%20Small%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Disney%20has%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsidethemagic.net%2F2023%2F08%2Fguests-weep-as-disney-world-closes-dinoland-zg1%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20will%20sunset%3C%2Fa%3E%20DinoLand%20USA%2C%20an%20older%20corner%20of%20Animal%20Kingdom%20that%20featured%20the%20kid-friendly%20Dinosaur%20ride.%20The%20parks%20have%20extended%20hours%20for%20late-night%20visitors%20through%20their%20%26quot%3BAfter%20Dark%26quot%3B%20events%2C%20and%20at%20Disneyland%20in%20California%2C%20the%20Anaheim%20parks%20introduced%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fattractionsmagazine.com%2Ffirst-ever-disneyland-after-dark-pride-nite-debuts-in-june%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einaugural%20Pride%20Nites%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20June.%20What's%20more%2C%20three%20new%20Disneyland%20restaurants%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Carnation%20Cafe%2C%20River%20Belle%20Terrace%2C%20and%20Cafe%20Orleans%20%E2%80%94%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc7.com%2Fdisneyland-drinks-alcohol-restaurants%2F13557556%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserving%20alcohol%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20guests%20in%20September.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20company%20has%20announced%20new%20holiday%20offerings%20at%20Disney%20World's%20Hollywood%20Studios%2C%20including%20a%20series%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdisneyparks.disney.go.com%2Fblog%2F2023%2F06%2Ffirst-look-new-holiday-party-at-disneys-hollywood-studios-mickeys-very-merry-christmas-party-2023-dates-revealed%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJollywood%20Nights%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20throughout%20November%20and%20December.%20The%20events%20%E2%80%94%20with%20ticket%20prices%20ranging%20from%20%24159%20to%20%24179%20per%20person%20%E2%80%94%20will%20feature%20a%20DJ%2C%20special%20cocktails%2C%20%26quot%3Bglitz%20and%20glamor%20galore%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20jazz%20lounge%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoiree%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Hollywood%20Tower%20Hotel%20Courtyard%2C%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Tower%20of%20Terror%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20unique%20experiences%20are%20casting%20a%20spell%20on%20millennial%20and%20Gen%20Z%20wallets.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20here%2C%20everything%20feels%20like%20it's%20laced%20with%20magic%20and%20truly%20pixie%20dust.%20Sure%2C%20we'll%20buy%20%2420%20drinks%20%E2%80%94%20but%20if%20we%20do%20that%20at%20a%20regular%20bar%2C%20I'm%20like%2C%20'That%20would%20be%20crazy.'%20But%20if%20it's%20at%20Disney%2C%20it's%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dominic%2C%20the%20TikTok%20influencer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20food%20and%20beverage%20offerings%2C%20high-end%20merch%20throughout%20the%20parks%20seems%20to%20speak%20to%20Disney's%20desire%20to%20capture%20these%20consumer%20dollars.%20At%20Hollywood%20Studios%2C%20sleek%20lightsabers%20like%20the%20blades%20wielded%20by%20iconic%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20characters%20such%20as%20Obi-Wan%20Kenobi%20and%20Emperor%20Palpatine%20retail%20for%20upward%20of%20%24200.%20One%20Disney%20World%20worker%20said%20she'd%20witnessed%20tears%20welling%20up%20in%20many%20adults'%20eyes%20the%20first%20time%20they%20activated%20their%20laser%20swords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20the%20merchandise%20front%2C%20Disney%20has%20launched%20multiple%20capsule%20collections%20in%20partnership%20with%20glossy%20brands%20like%20Gucci%2C%20Dooney%20%26amp%3B%20Bourke%2C%20and%20Coach%2C%20emblazoning%20Disney%20iconography%20on%20everything%20from%20jeans%20to%20accessories%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db70728b4ba8bbfc221ef45b93201ee48553f2bf663228a88866712e569fddb4f%26postID%3D64baf83e52829be1d3671056%26postSlug%3Dwhy-disney-parks-top-destinations-millennials-gen-z-2023-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.shopdisney.com%252Fmickey-mouse-and-friends-backpack-by-coach-195031823565.html%253FCMP%253DKNC-DSSGoogle%2526efc%253D179006%2526CMP%253DKNC-DSS_FY23_DCR_TRA_DOM_EVGR_ECM_GNRL_PMAX%25257CG%25257C1199623.SRC.03%25257CMF9MFIS%2526gclid%253DEAIaIQobChMIldixrrGogQMVAAytBh0Mog6HEAQYASABEgKk2vD_BwE%2526gclsrc%253Daw.ds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoach%20backpack%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20nearly%20%24600.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20celebration%20of%20Disney%20World's%2050th%20anniversary%2C%20merch%20designers%20from%20across%20the%20company%20worked%20on%20developing%20styles%20that%20would%20appeal%20to%20older%20shoppers%2C%20the%20former%20Disney%20travel%20marketing%20executive%20recalled.%20Many%20items%20intentionally%20emphasized%20fresh%20color%20schemes%20or%20iridescence%20to%20appeal%20to%20a%20customer%20with%20%26quot%3Bmore%20sophisticated%26quot%3B%20tastes%2C%20this%20former%20exec%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Hey%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20adults%20in%20the%20parks.%20We%20haven't%20met%20a%20single%20kid%20today%2C'%20cast%20members%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20has%20had%20its%20eye%20on%20this%20demographic%20and%20its%20spending%20power%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20company%20piloted%20a%20campaign%20called%20%23HappyPlace%2C%20which%20mainly%20consisted%20of%20a%20series%20of%20videos%20incubated%20by%20teams%20at%20Yellow%20Shoes%2C%20Disney's%20internal%20advertising%20agency%20devoted%20to%20parks%2C%20experiences%2C%20and%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%23HappyPlace%20content%20was%20geared%20toward%20childless%20adults%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20above%20the%20drinking%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neph%20Trejo%2C%20a%20creative%20director%20who%20worked%20for%20Disney%20until%20earlier%20this%20summer%20and%20was%20integral%20to%20the%20campaign's%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20showcased%20what%20a%20trip%20to%20Disney%20World%20without%20children%20could%20look%20like%20for%20adult%20friend%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20including%20sipping%20on%20sake%20and%20feasting%20on%20fresh%20gyros.%20One%20video%20posted%20to%20Trejo's%20website%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BSwag%20Safari%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20to%20a%20moody%20soundtrack%20and%20portrays%20a%20fictionalized%20trip%20to%20Animal%20Kingdom%20in%20which%20a%20handful%20of%20millennials%20embark%20on%20the%20Kilimanjaro%20Safari%20and%2C%20from%20a%20high-end%20hotel%20terrace%2C%20watch%20giraffes%20wake%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20approach%20was%20to%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20the%20beautiful%20tapestry%20of%20people%20that%20come%20to%20Walt%20Disney%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20Trejo%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20about%20rides.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20churros.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20Dole%20Whip%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20parks'%20famous%20frozen-pineapple%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Halle%20Bailey%20performs%20at%20Disney%20World%20for%20ABC's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Most%20Magical%20Story%20On%20Earth%26quot%3B%20special%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650272d9992da60019ebfeb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHalle%20Bailey%20performs%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World's%2050th%20anniversary%20celebration%20in%202021.%3Cp%3EKent%20Phillips%2FABC%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20Disney%20characters%20are%20fielding%20hugs%20and%20selfies%20with%20grown-up%20customers%20these%20days.%20One%20Disney%20World%20employee%20said%20lines%20to%20meet%20iconic%20characters%20can%20sometimes%20be%20made%20up%20of%20half%20or%20more%20adults%20without%20children.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20adults%20in%20the%20parks.%20We%20haven't%20met%20a%20single%20kid%20today%2C'%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said.%20%26quot%3BOr%2C%20'I%20was%20just%20out%20there%20for%20an%20hour%20and%20I%20saw%20three%20kids%20the%20entire%20time%20of%20the%20two%20to%20three%20hundred%20people%20I%20met.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20darker%20side%20of%20this%20demo%20that's%20created%20pain%20points%20for%20some%20Disney%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20visitors%20get%20a%20thrill%20from%20performing%20stunts%20seemingly%20conjured%20to%20go%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20On%20TikTok%2C%20examples%20are%20plentiful%20of%20teenagers%20and%2020-somethings%20physically%20touching%20or%20recording%20cast%20members%2C%20asking%20personal%20questions%20to%20try%20to%20break%20their%20unflappable%20depictions%20of%20figures%20like%20Cinderella.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40igotz2p%2Fvideo%2F7271288169398570283%3F_r%3D1%26_t%3D8ffHGJJ15qt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20a%20woman%20laying%20her%20hands%20on%20the%20chest%20of%20an%20actor%20playing%20Gaston%20from%20%26quot%3BBeauty%20and%20the%20Beast.%26quot%3B%20The%20Disney%20World%20employee%20recalled%20a%20guest%20who%20broke%20park%20rules%20by%20lapping%20water%20from%20decorative%20fountains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManagement%20has%20addressed%20the%20situation%20in%20private%20conversations%20with%20parks%20talent%2C%20according%20to%20the%20employee%2C%20who%20said%20Disney%20World%20has%20adopted%20a%20strict%20policy%20that%20its%20actors%20refrain%20from%20participating%20in%20social-media%20trends.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20absolutely%20step%20away%20or%20you%20can%20ask%20for%20a%20leadership%20position%20to%20come%20over%20and%20chat%20with%20them%20if%20it's%20something%20that's%20uncomfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said%2C%20describing%20the%20company's%20guidance.%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20internet%20these%20days%2C%20everything%20you%20do%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20put%20online%20at%20some%20point%2C%20so%20be%20aware%20of%20that.%20So%20it's%20definitely%20something%20they%20touch%20on%20in%20our%20training.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20though%2C%20the%20parks%20worker%20says%20the%20uptick%20in%20adult%20attendees%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20open%20road%20for%20new%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20cater%20to%20an%20older%20crowd%20because%20you%20can%20better%20know%20their%20wants%20and%20needs%2C%20whereas%20with%20kids%2C%20kids%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20they%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20employee%20explained%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20customer-experience%20surveys%20Disney%20sends%20visitors.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20the%20adults'%20opinions%20who%20they%20care%20about%20and%20who%20they're%20trying%20to%20cater%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'There%20is%20a%20tug%20of%20war%20from%20adult%20to%20family%20at%20times%2C'%20says%20a%20former%20Disney%20Imagineer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Singh%20loved%20classic%20Disney%20movies%20growing%20up%20and%20still%20recalls%20the%20first%20time%20he%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20parks%20at%20age%2012.%20He%20felt%20an%20instant%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20from%20that%20first%20trip%20that%20I'd%20found%20my%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20it%2C%20how%20it%20came%20to%20be%2C%20how%20everything%20worked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20Singh%20couldn't%20have%20predicted%20that%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20he'd%20have%20relocated%20to%20Orlando%2C%20where%20his%20fascination%20with%20theme%20parks%20would%20blossom%20into%20a%20career.%20Now%2C%20as%20a%20content%20creator%20focused%20on%20Disney%20World%2C%20Singh%2C%2023%2C%20has%20amassed%20a%20million%20followers%20on%20his%20JeremyTheTea%20TikTok%20page%2C%20and%20has%20been%20hired%20by%20Disney%20in%20what%20he%20said%20is%20a%20bid%20to%20reach%20this%20prized%20young-adult%20demographic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20when%20I'm%20called%20to%20do%20these%20things%2C%20they're%20probably%20trying%20to%20get%20to%20that%20audience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Singh%2C%20noting%20that%20his%20primary%20following%20ranges%20between%2021%20and%2028%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20actors'%20strike%2C%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-lost-deals-thousands-during-actors-strike-jasmine-paige-moore-2023-8%5C%22%3Eparalyzed%20the%20promotion%20of%20most%20new%20films%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20movie%20stars%20and%20online%20content%20creators%20alike%2C%20Singh%20helped%20support%20marketing%20efforts%20surrounding%20Disney's%20live-action%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Mermaid%26quot%3B%20film%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20attended%20a%20Disneyland%20performance%20by%20the%20movie's%20lead%20actor%20Halle%20Bailey%20that%20was%20broadcast%20on%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Idol.%26quot%3B%20He's%20also%20been%20tapped%20to%20promote%20Disney's%20Halloween%20festivities%2C%20which%20he%20said%20would%20tie%20into%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BHaunted%20Mansion%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-used-park-actors-for-haunted-mansion-premiere-amid-strike-2023-7%5C%22%3Efilm%20premiere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20eponymous%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%20has%20become%20a%20leading%20voice%20within%20a%20burgeoning%20community%20of%20Disney-focused%20influencers%20that%20emerged%20during%20the%20pandemic%20years%20and%2C%20according%20to%20experts%2C%20has%20helped%20fuel%20adults'%20interest%20in%20the%20parks.%20A%20search%20for%20the%20term%20%23DisneyWorld%20on%20TikTok%20reveals%20that%20the%20hashtag%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20content%20viewed%20some%2020%20billion%20times%2C%20while%20Disney%20Parks'%20own%20TikTok%20page%20has%20surpassed%205.7%20million%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancis%20Dominic%2C%20the%20former%20parks%20worker%20turned%20influencer%2C%20has%20also%20been%20tapped%20to%20promote%20Disney%20parks%20and%20films.%20He%20cohosted%20an%20advanced%20screening%20of%20Disney%20and%20Pixar's%20%26quot%3BElemental%26quot%3B%20this%20year%20alongside%20Patrick%20Dougall%2C%20another%20Disney%20creator%20who's%20built%20up%20a%20TikTok%20following%20of%20380%2C000.%20Attendees%20%E2%80%94%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20whom%20were%20millennials%20%E2%80%94%20were%20asked%20to%20dress%20as%20their%20favorite%20element%20inspired%20by%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20Disney%20makes%20a%20concerted%20push%20to%20keep%20this%20all-important%20audience%20coming%20back%2C%20some%20warn%20that%20the%20parks%20can't%20afford%20to%20alienate%20their%20other%20vital%20fandom%3A%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20tug%20of%20war%20from%20adult%20to%20family%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Eades%2C%20a%20former%20Disney%20Imagineer%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20early%20'90s%20who's%20watched%20the%20brand%20evolve%20over%20the%20decades.%20Unless%20Disney%20can%20find%20an%20equilibrium%20that%20keeps%20both%20groups%20happy%2C%20Eades%20cautioned%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they'll%20realize%2C%20'Uh-oh%2C%20we've%20left%20the%20kids%20at%20