2%3Ebeen%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fdoctors-flag-poor-living-conditions-in-manipur-relief-camps%2Farticle67270164.ece%5C%22%3Earriving%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20look%20at%20the%20media!%20Did%20a%20single%20one%20of%20us%20ask%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20who%20otherwise%20visits%20the%20region%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmodi-discovered-ashta-lakshmi-in-8-ne-states-sonowal%2F832701%2F%5C%22%3Ecalls%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CAstha%20Lakshmi%E2%80%9D%20several%20times%20during%20the%20election%20season%2C%20why%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care%20to%20visit%20a%20state%20in%20deep%20turmoil%20and%20ruled%20by%20his%20party%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20strange%20that%20the%20media%20has%20no%20access%20at%20all%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9CMother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%20media%20is%20sold%20out%20to%20the%20establishment%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20seem%20to%20have%20internalised%20the%20need%20to%20discipline%20our%20minds%20by%20not%20offending%20the%20power%20holders%20because%20the%20consequences%20are%20fearful%20to%20contemplate.%20But%20how%20did%20we%20arrive%20at%20this%20juncture%20and%20where%20is%20the%20spirit%20to%20fight%20the%20demons%20that%20are%20chipping%20away%20at%20the%20democratic%20pillars%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fat-least-194-journalists-were-targeted-across-india-in-2022-report%5C%22%3EAt%20Least%20194%20Journalists%20Were%20Targeted%20Across%20India%20in%202022%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20media%20coverage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20turn%20our%20attention%20to%20Manipur%20and%20the%20media%20coverage%20from%20the%20troubled%20state.%20One%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20the%20mental%2C%20emotional%2C%20social%2C%20and%20political%20divide%20between%20the%20tribes%2C%20occupying%20the%20hills%20of%20Manipur%20and%20those%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20from%20the%20region%20who%20flit%20in%20and%20out%20of%20these%20seven%20states%20for%20varying%20reasons%20have%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20the%20cultural%20and%20ethnic%20sensitivities%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20journalists%20flying%20into%20Manipur%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20with%20tight%20deadlines%20to%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20depends%20who%20the%20journalists%20speak%20to%20and%20whether%20they%20have%20figured%20out%20that%20at%20this%20juncture%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98sane%E2%80%99%20voice%20that%20can%20give%20them%20a%20non-partisan%2C%20objective%20account%20of%20things%20as%20they%20play%20out%20on%20the%20ground.%20Talk%20to%20one%20group%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20account%3B%20talk%20to%20the%20other%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20carefully%20curated%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20a%20journalist%2C%20without%20any%20training%20in%20conflict%20reporting%2C%20operate%20in%20a%20region%20that%20has%20never%20really%20been%20psychologically%20and%20emotionally%20integrated%20with%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20who%20really%20waits%20for%20the%20traditional%2Flegacy%20media%20these%20days%3F%20People%20avariciously%20consume%20social%20media%20and%20YouTubers%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20present%20their%20narratives%2C%20often%20without%20mediation%20or%20language%20moderation.%20Reading%20the%20news%20that%20is%20edited%20in%20New%20Delhi%20or%20elsewhere%20feels%20bland%20to%20those%20that%20have%20learnt%20to%20rely%20on%20instant%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20another%20section%20of%20the%20media%20that%20has%20been%20told%20by%20their%20editors%20what%20to%20look%20for%20and%20why.%20In%20these%20polarised%20times%2C%20the%20media%20has%20taken%20a%20big%20hit%20but%20journalists%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20the%20moral%20courage%20to%20fight%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeveral%20instances%20of%20discrimination%2C%20but%20no%20questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20Internet%20ban%20is%20not%20uniformly%20applied%20and%20seems%20to%20favour%20one%20group%20against%20another.%20To%20meet%20their%20deadlines%2C%20reporters%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20IPR%20office%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%20to%20send%20their%20news%20across.%20This%20would%20mean%20that%20Imphal%20still%20had%20a%20semblance%20of%20internet%20connectivity%3B%20the%20hills%20were%20completely%20cut%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20both%20groups%20have%20learnt%20to%20control%20the%20narratives%20and%20project%20themselves%20as%20victims.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20hill%20tribes%20are%20more%20badly%20affected%20due%20to%20logistical%20disadvantages.%20They%20also%20have%20no%20outlet%20outside%20Manipur%2C%20except%20through%20Mizoram%2C%20which%20requires%20a%20lengthy%20drive%20on%20what%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98offroad%E2%80%99%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20noted%20singer%20and%20lyricist%2C%20Mangboi%20Lhumdin%2C%20who%20also%20was%20a%20village%20volunteer%20along%20with%20four%20others%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur%2Ftwo-succumb-to-injuries-as-fresh-firing-reported-from-manipur-2667410%5C%22%3Edied%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20bomb%20attack.%20Lhumding%20was%20taken%20to%20Mizoram%20for%20treatment%20but%20died%20on%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20the%20two%20Kuki-Zo%20women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Eparaded%20naked%3C%2Fa%3E%20shook%20the%20conscience%20of%20this%20country%20and%20the%20world%2C%20but%20even%20that%20was%20short-lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fthe-manipur-crisis-in-numbers-four-months-of-unending-violence%5C%22%3EThe%20Manipur%20Crisis%20in%20Numbers%3A%20Four%20Months%20of%20Unending%20Violence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20G20%20member%20wanted%20to%20ask%20any%20questions%20on%20that%20horrific%20video.%20They%20were%20probably%20all%20bamboozled%20to%20ask%20only%20diplomatically%20correct%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20discrimination%20meted%20out%20to%20tribal%20students%20by%20the%20Manipur%20University%20was%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20Out%20of%2076%20students%20studying%20Psychology%20in%20Rayburn%20College%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehillsjournal.com%2Fmanipulation-or-error-manipur-university-examination-results-for-rayburn-college-draws-flak-from-all-quarters%2F%5C%22%3Eonly%2010%20students%20passed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20complained%20to%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20the%20results%20were%20reviewed%20and%20drastically%20changed%20within%20two%20to%20three%20hours.%20The%20number%20of%20passed%20students%20went%20up%20from%2010%20to%2041.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ITLF%20has%20asked%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20comprehensive%20audit%20of%20the%20results%20and%20transfer%20the%20tribal%20students%20to%20other%20reputed%20state%20universities.%20It%20is%20evident%20now%20that%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20(students%2C%20office-goers%2C%20university%20employees%2C%20etc.)%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20their%20jobs%2Funiversity%2Fbusinesses%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20next%20question.%20Will%20the%20Imphal%20valley%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20a%20hub%20of%20diversity%20for%20as%20long%20as%20we%20can%20remember%20%E2%80%93%20become%20an%20exclusive%20home%20of%20the%20Meteis%3F%20Is%20diversity%20going%20to%20be%20lost%20forever%3F%20How%20do%20people%20of%20the%20same%20state%20be%20divided%20by%20barricades%20and%20bunkers%20where%20each%20side%20sees%20the%20other%20as%20the%20enemy%3F%20Who%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20first%20to%20smoke%20the%20peace%20pipe%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%20the%20Nagas%20are%20waiting%20and%20watching%20the%20developments.%20There%20is%20no%20knowing%20what%20the%20Naga%20reaction%20will%20be%20if%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20dig%20in%20their%20heels%20on%20the%20separate%20administration%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffull-text-manipur-crisis-gk-pillai-karan-thapar%5C%22%3EFull%20Text%20%7C%20Manipur%20Crisis%3A%20Steps%20That%20Should%20Have%20Been%20Taken%20and%20Should%20Be%20Taken%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20has%20forgotten%20to%20remind%20our%20audience%20of%20the%20torture%20meted%20out%20to%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20adviser%2C%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20Kuki%20MLA%2C%20Vungzagin%20Valte%2C%20who%20is%20partially%20paralysed%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBDUdgrrEvzc%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20by%20far%20we%20failed%20in%20our%20journalistic%20ethics%20when%20we%20reported%20what%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20(SG)%2C%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-most-unclaimed-bodies-lying-in-morgues-are-of-infiltrators-government-tells-supreme-court-news-307387%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20bodies%20lying%20unclaimed%20in%20the%20morgues%20are%20those%20of%20infiltrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20SG%20establish%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20dead%3F%20Should%20the%20media%20not%20have%20questioned%20that%20report%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%20the%20media%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20answer.%20Although%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20media%20have%20provided%20analytical%20coverage%2C%20offering%20read