y%20and%20the%20rights%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ronga%2C%20a%20senior%20lawyer%20who%20filed%20the%20petition%20at%20the%20high%20court%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20the%20petition%20states%20that%20two%20police%20vehicles%20and%20security%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20outside%20Mirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20Nigeen%20locality%20curtailing%20his%20movement%20by%20using%20powers%20%E2%80%9Cunknown%20to%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20been%20deprived%20of%20his%20fundamental%20rights%20guaranteed%20to%20him%20under%20Article%2019%20and%2021%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%20has%20%E2%80%9Csuffered%20illegal%20confinement%20in%20a%20most%20unjustified%20and%20illegal%20manner%20which%20amounts%20to%20misuse%20of%20power%20and%20authority%E2%80%9D%20while%20causing%20%E2%80%9Cmental%20agony%E2%80%9D%20to%20him%20as%20his%20detention%20has%20affected%20his%20entire%20family%2C%20according%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20which%20asserts%20that%20the%20Hurriyat%20leader%20has%20a%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20claim%20compensation%20and%20damages%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20governor%20Sinha%20has%20denied%20that%20Mirwaiz%20was%20under%20curbs%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20to%20go%20wherever%20he%20likes%E2%80%9D.%20The%20petition%2C%20however%2C%20states%20that%20Mirwaiz%20tried%20to%20come%20out%20of%20his%20house%20after%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20statement%20and%20attend%20congregational%20Friday%20prayers%20at%20Jamia%20Masjid%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20August%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20petition%2C%20while%20pointing%20to%20photographic%20evidence%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20news%20reports%2C%20claims%20that%20Mirwaiz%20was%20stopped%20from%20leaving%20his%20house%20even%20after%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20assurance%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20petitioner%20is%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20move%20or%20to%20attend%20the%20congregational%20prayers%20on%20Fridays%20at%20Jamia%20Masiid%2C%20Srinagar%2C%20therefore%20%E2%80%A6.%20(his)%20religious%20rights%20are%20also%20infringed%20in%20violation%20of%20Articles%2025-28%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2011-page%20petition%20terms%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%E2%80%99s%20stand%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconcocted%20story%E2%80%9D%20while%20accusing%20it%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpropagating%20misinformation%E2%80%9D%20about%20Mirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20(administration%20has)%20%E2%80%A6%20been%20on%20one%20hand%20detaining%20the%20petitioner%20illegally%20and%20unauthorisedly%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20have%20been%20claiming%20that%20the%20petitioner%20is%20free%20to%20move%20anywhere%20else%20he%20wants%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20notes%2C%20while%20urging%20the%20court%20to%20appoint%20a%20judicial%20officer%20for%20%E2%80%9Cspot%20inspection%E2%80%9D%20of%20Mirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20residence%20to%20%E2%80%9Cascertain%20the%20actual%20position.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20chief%20cleric%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20Mirwaiz%2C%20whose%20father%2C%20Molvi%20Mohammad%20Farooq%2C%20was%20assassinated%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20May%2021%2C%201990%2C%20legislated%20on%20religious%20matters%20and%20also%20led%20prayers%20on%20Fridays%20and%20other%20significant%20religious%20days%20at%20the%20historic%20Jamia%20Masjid%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20largest%20mosque%20located%20in%20Nowhatta%20locality%20of%20downtown%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20states%20that%20Mirwaiz%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20advocate%20of%20peace%20not%20only%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20but%20also%20in%20the%20entire%20sub-continent%E2%80%9D%20who%20believes%20in%20%E2%80%9Cuniversal%20brotherhood%2C%20religious%20tolerance%20and%20coexistence%E2%80%9D%20and%20promotes%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20values%20and%20eradication%20of%20social%20ills%20in%20the%20society%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20confining%20him%2C%20he%20has%20not%20only%20being%20deprived%20of%20his%20noble%20mission%20and%20cause%20but%20such%20illegal%20action%20of%20respondents%20are%20also%20depriving%20hundred%20and%20thousands%20of%20people%20from%20listening%20to%20his%20inspiring%20Friday%20sermons%20and%20the%20sermons%20he%20delivers%20across%20the%20valley%20on%20important%20religious%20occasions%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20states%2C%20terming%20Mirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20detention%20as%C2%A0%C2%A0a%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20attempt%20to%20hurt%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20legal%20notice%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20going%20unanswered%2C%20the%20petition%20notes%20that%20Mirwaiz%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Ccondemned%20unheard%20which%20is%20against%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20also%20points%20to%20a%20letter%20of%20Mutahida%20Mailis-e-Ulema%2C%20an%20amalgam%20of%20religious%20organisations%2C%20which%20had%20on%20August%2013%20sought%20an%20appointment%20with%20LG%20Sinha%20to%20seek%20his%20intervention%20in%20the%20release%20of%20Mirwaiz.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20letter%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20urges%20the%20high%20court%20to%20issue%20%E2%80%9Ca%20writ%2C%20order%20or%20direction%2C%20directing%20the%20respondents%20not%20to%20create%20any%20impediments%20into%20the%20day-to-day%20life%20of%20the%20petitioner%20including%20his%20free%20movement%20as%20a%20citizen%20and%20allow%20him%20to%20perform%20and%20enjoy%20the%20freedom%20and%20liberty%20guaranteed%20to%20petitioner%20under%20the%20constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694780429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-co