0data%3F%20We%20used%20to%20send%20our%20people%20to%20states%20where%20elections%20were%20held.%20Has%20history%20stopped%3F%20Have%20elections%20stopped%3F%20Has%20democracy%20stopped%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Quraishi%20about%20the%20merger%20on%20call%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Edict.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpotlight%3A%20support%20and%20criticism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJournalists%20and%20political%20commentators%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20to%20express%20their%20support%20and%20appreciation%20for%20the%20TCPD%20after%20the%20board%E2%80%99s%20letter%20went%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20journalist%20who%20does%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20stories%20around%20Indian%20elections%2C%20I%20will%20always%20be%20grateful%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGillesVerniers%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%40GillesVerniers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20team%20at%20TCPD%20for%20the%20public%20good%20they%20built%20in%20the%20form%20of%20their%20open%20source%20dataset%20on%20elections.%20Hope%20that%20their%20good%20work%20carries%20on%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Roshan%20Kishore%2C%20Data%20and%20Political%20Economy%20Editor%20at%20Hindustan%20Times%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRoshanjnu%2Fstatus%2F1701506052204925147%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGillesVerniers%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40GillesVerniers%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20work%20has%20been%20unparalleled%20for%20opening%20up%20Indian%20politics%20to%20data.%20I%20have%20personally%20benefited%20from%20his%20work%20so%20much%20and%20it%20informs%20so%20much%20of%20my%20writing%20on%20politics%E2%80%9D%2