t%20Shah%20had%20assured%20the%20Meitei%20community%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20separate%20administration%20and%20separation%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20he%20would%20resolve%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20within%2010%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Nganbi%20made%20any%20requests%20of%20Shah%2C%20she%20said%20there%20were%20quite%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20asked%20him%20to%20bring%20peace%20to%20Manipur%2C%20to%20stop%20poppy%20cultivation%2C%20to%20stop%20narco-terrorism%2C%20to%20develop%20a%20good%20education%20system%20in%20Manipur%2C%20to%20help%20people%20return%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20cancel%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20%5Bwith%20hill-based%20insurgent%20organisations%5D%2C%20and%20many%20other%20things.%20But%20after%20he%20left%20Imphal%2C%20attacks%20on%20Meitei%20increased%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20he%20encouraged%20Kuki%20to%20attack%20us%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002-300x266.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002-1024x908.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221064%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMera%20Paibis%20outside%20the%20Bishnupur%20DC%20Office%20in%20May.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Accomplices%20in%20a%20number%20of%20rape%20FIRs%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENganbi%20also%20claimed%20that%20Meitei%20people%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Clooted%20in%20Churachandpur%E2%80%9D%20by%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20militants%20who%20were%20under%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%E2%80%9D%20She%20further%20added%20that%20women%20on%20the%20Meitei%20community%20had%20been%20raped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuki%20community%20members%20have%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20Meiteis%20who%20have%20attacked%20Kukis%20disproportionately.%20In%20July%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20Meitei%20mob%20and%20being%20sexually%20assaulted%20had%20garnered%20nationwide%20outrage.%20More%20women%20have%20since%20come%20forward%2C%20essaying%20accounts%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeira%20Paibis%E2%80%99%20names%20are%20registered%20as%20accomplices%20in%20a%20number%20of%20first%20information%20reports%20alleging%20rapes%20and%20sexual%20assault%20against%20Kuki%20community%20women.%20From%20their%20historic%20Kangla%20Fort%20protest%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20against%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20to%20this%20point%20in%20time%20where%20many%20have%20alleged%20that%20they%20have%20a%20role%20in%20the%20sexual%20crimes%20perpetrated%20against%20Kuki%20women%2C%20are%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20still%20going%20to%20present%20themselves%20as%20ones%20standing%20for%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20women%3F%20Nangbi%20says%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20against%20everyone%20who%20is%20doing%20wrong%20in%20our%20state%20%E2%80%93%20no%20matter%20which%20ethnicity%20they%20are%20from.%20Two%20Kuki%20women%20were%20paraded%20naked%20but%20the%20ones%20who%20helped%20them%20survive%20and%20gave%20them%20clothes%20were%20Meira%20Paibis.%20We%20condemn%20such%20instances%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20that%20this%20incident%20should%20be%20investigated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nganbi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%20and%20Union%20governments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENganbi%20lives%20around%2030%20km%20away%20from%20Churachandpur%20in%20Bishnupur%20district.%20Since%20May%203%2C%20there%20has%20almost%20been%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20internet%20in%20the%20state.%20Nganbi%20said%20that%20she%20was%20getting%20all%20her%20information%20from%20Churachandpur%20through%20her%20phone.%20She%20is%20critical%20of%20both%20the%20governments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20Manipur%20were%20seeking%20help%20from%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20government%2C%20but%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20any%20help%20from%20them.%20Instead%2C%20attacks%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20have%20increased.%20We%20ourselves%20are%20helping%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nganbi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Kuki%20community%20members%20have%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20administration%20for%20favouring%20Meiteis%2C%20Nganbi%20is%20not%20impressed%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20situation%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Manipur%20government%20is%20the%20puppet%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%20They%20do%20what%20the%20Union%20government%20wants%20them%20to%20do.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20silent%20for%20months%20when%20houses%20of%20our%20community%20were%20being%20attacked%20by%20Kuki%20militants%20and%20our%20women%20were%20being%20raped%2C%20only%20spoke%20when%20a%20video%20of%20two%20went%20viral.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20condition%20has%20been%20in%20turmoil%20since%20May%203.%20Meiteis%20had%20felt%20left%20out%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20because%20he%20never%20spoke%20a%20word%20for%20our%20community.%20For%20today%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20are%20completely%20responsible%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20they%20are%20out%20to%20end%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20the%20Meitei%20community%20has%20alleged%20that%20security%20forces%20have%20helped%20Kuki%20militants%20in%20this%20conflict%2C%20while%20Kuki%20community%20members%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20law%20enforcement%20has%20helped%20Meitei%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%5C%22%3EManipur%20Police%20Files%20FIR%20Against%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20%E2%80%98Allowing%20Kuki%20Militants%20to%20Flee%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20Meira%20Paibis%20against%20the%20central%20security%20forces%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20asks%20Nangbi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%20of%20the%202004%20protests%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20had%20raped%20our%20sisters.%20Several%20women%20came%20out%20and%20spoke%2C%20but%20some%20decided%20to%20remain%20silent%20forever%2C%20like%20Rose%20Ningshen%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20by%20BSF%20officers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%204%2C%201974%2C%20Ningshen%20was%20raped%20by%20Border%20Security%20Forces%20officers%2C%20and%20two%20days%20later%2C%20died%20by%20suicide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20unforgettable%20and%20heart-wrenching%20incident%20is%20that%20of%20Thangjam%20Manorama.%20Manorama%20was%20picked%20up%20from%20her%20house%20by%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20front%20of%20her%20family%2C%20they%20raped%20her%2C%20and%20later%20shot%20at%20her%20private%20parts.%20Since%20then%2C%20we%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20all%20central%20forces%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20Meira%20Paibis%20have%20to%20take%20care%20of%20our%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nangbi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAssam%20Rifles%20had%20been%20using%20their%20powers%20wrongly%20for%20years%3B%20if%20they%20wanted%2C%20they%20could%20have%20controlled%20the%20situation%20on%20May%203%20itself%20when%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694772605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145950%2Fnangbi-e1694771180308.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmeira-paibi-interview-central-forces-rape-allegation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lourembam%20Nganbi%2C%20a%20Meira%20Paibi%20leader%2C%20had%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20naked%20protest%20against%20the%20Army%20after%20the%20rape%20and%20killing%20of%20Thangjam%20Manorama%20in%202004.%20Now%2C%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20are%20named%20accomplices%20in%20several%20rape%20cases%20since%20May%203.%20Nganbi%20speaks%20on%20the%20allegations%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmeira-paibi-interview-central-forces-rape-allegation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Successful%20Critical%20Interrogation%20of%20India's%20Justice%20System%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15151528%2Fhammer-620011_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUnsealed%20Covers%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20essays%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findconlawphil.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Indian%20Constitutional%20Law%20and%20philosophy%20blog%2C%20a%20legal%20resource%20that%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20has%20become%20an%20almost%20universal%20reference%20for%20law%20students%2C%20lawyers%2C%20academics%20and%20almost%20anyone%20interested%20in%20legal%20developments.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20constitutional%20bench%20hearings%20are%20streaming%20on%20news%20channels%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20in%20front%20and%20centre%20of%20the%20political%20discourse%20in%20the%20country%2C%20author%20Gautam%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20work%20(in%20this%20book%20and%20otherwise)%20has%20allowed%20us%20entry%20into%20courtrooms%2C%20often%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day%20as%20a%20verdict%2C%20and%20get%20a%20fly%20on%20the%20wall%20view%20of%20the%20wheels%20of%20justice%20turning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20benefited%20from%20the%20blog%20on%20numerous%20occasions%2C%20both%20to%20clarify%20and%20understand%20important%20questions%20of%20law%20as%20well%20as%20to%20use%20as%20a%20source%20of%20research%20and%20analysis%20in%20a%20time%20of%20crisis%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20strikes%20the%20reader%20about%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20writing%20is%20how%20each%20article%20(individual%20blog%20posts%20reproduced%20in%20the%20book%20have%20been%20referred%20to%20as%20articles%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20review)%20breaks%20down%20intricate%20legal%20cases%20and%20principles%2C%20offering%20readers%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20their%20significance%20and%20implications.%20Even%20for%20those%20without%20a%20legal%20background%2C%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20explanations%20are%20enlightening%20and%20allow%20for%20engagement%20with%20both%20the%20process%20and%20the%20substance%20of%20adjudication%20in%20the%20Appellate%20courts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20212px)%2085vw%2C%20212px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145501%2Fimage-1316-212x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22212%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145501%2Fimage-1316-212x300.png%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145501%2Fimage-1316.png%20432w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673182%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUnsealed%20Covers%3A%20A%20Decade%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Courts%20and%20the%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20(HarperCollins%20India%2C%20August%2010%2C%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20to%20this%2C%20the%20sheer%20breadth%20of%20issues%20that%20Bhatia%20has%20managed%20to%20cover%20in%20a%20lucid%20and%20yet%20information%20laden%20prose%20(the%20book%20informs%20you%20that%20the%20posts%20covered%20within%20it%20are%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20number%20of%20blog%20posts)%20is%20remarkable.%20The%20book%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20parts%3A%20rights%2C%20constitutional%20structure%2C%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20each%20article%20covers%20a%20judgment%20(or%20a%20set%20of%20judgments)%20corresponding%20with%20the%20larger%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20part%20is%20the%20heavily%20contested%20terrain%20of%20%E2%80%98rights%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20Bhatia%20takes%20a%20largely%20scathing%20view%20of%20how%20courts%20in%20the%20past%20decade%20have%20responded%20when%20asked%20questions%20about%20personal%20liberty%2C%20citizenship%2C%20the%20demolition%20of%20homes%20among%20many%20others.%20This%20is%20notwithstanding%20some%20notable%20exceptions%20such%20as%20the%20judgments%20for%20reservations%20in%20promotions%2C%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20judgments%20(with%20a%20note%20of%20caution%20on%20how%20the%20principles%20contained%20within%20are%20operationalised%20by%20subsequent%20courts%2C%20which%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20prophetic)%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20overruling%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kaushal%20to%20hold%20that%20members%20of%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20are%20equally%20entitled%20to%20rights%20under%20Part%20III%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20theme%20which%20emerges%20from%20this%20part%2C%20and%20one%20that%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20by%20other%20authors%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20is%20a%20judicial%20roulette%20or%20lottery%E2%80%94%20where%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20liberty%20(or%20the%20lack%20of%20it)%20or%20indeed%20the%20burden%20of%20establishing%20citizenship%20%E2%80%94%20may%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20simple%20chance%20(or%20design)%20of%20which%20bench%20your%20case%20is%20listed%20before.%20This%20may%20be%20an%20unavoidable%20consequence%20of%20a%20court%20with%2032%20sitting%20judges%20(usually%20sitting%20in%20combinations%20of%20two%20or%20three%20judges)%2C%20but%20it%20does%20leave%20room%20to%20desire%20greater%20judicial%20consistency%2C%20especially%20in%20matters%20where%20individual%20citizens%20or%20marginalised%20communities%20have%20approached%20the%20courts%20seeking%20hope%20of%20liberty%20and%20due%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20work%20may%20possibly%20spew%20allegations%20ranging%20from%20it%20being%20borne%20out%20of%20activist%20lawyering%2C%20but%20to%20his%20credit%2C%20Bhatia%20is%20not%20one%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20praise%20of%20judgments%20and%20dissents%20that%20according%20to%20him%20follow%20constitutional%20doctrine%20and%20lead%20to%20expansion%20of%20rights.%20One%20of%20the%20many%20themes%20emerging%20from%20his%20work%20is%20the%20notion%20that%20it%20is%20only%20through%20deliberative%20dialogue%20that%20the%20transformative%20vision%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20makers%20can%20be%20achieved%2C%20and%20any%20attempt%20to%20fetter%20this%20dialogue%2C%20rather%20than%20protecting%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20judicial%20apparatus%2C%20in%20fact%20only%20serves%20to%20weaken%20its%20foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjudiciary-in-the-modi-era-shielding-the-state-and-axing-the-people%5C%22%3EJudiciary%20in%20the%20Modi%20Era%3A%20Shielding%20the%20State%20and%20Leaving%20the%20People%20Vulnerable%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20book%20deals%20with%20questions%20of%20federalism%2C%20anti-defection%20laws%20and%20the%20Right%20to%20Information.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20fresh%20off%20a%20marathon%2016-day%20hearing%20of%20the%20various%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20power%20and%20procedure%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%3B%20and%20in%20the%20past%20year%20alone%20has%20delivered%20judgments%20regarding%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20power%20over%20administrative%20services%20in%20the%20capital%20status%20of%20the%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%20(%3Cem%3EGovt%20of%20NCT%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20modifying%20the%20process%20of%20appointing%20members%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20(%3Cem%3EAnoop%20Baranwal%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20on%20the%20rift%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20manner%20of%20functioning%20of%20the%20governor%20and%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20in%20Maharashtra%20(%3Cem%3ESubhash%20Desai%20v.%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20Governor%20of%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20positions%20of%20law%20enunciated%20in%20%E2%80%98Govt%20of%20NCT%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Anoop%20Baranwal%E2%80%99%20have%20since%20been%20altered%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20through%20the%20introduction%20of%20an%20Ordinance%20and%20a%20Bill%2C%20respectively.%20This%20highlights%20the%20tripartite%20tension%20that%20exists%20between%20the%20consolidation%20of%20power%20in%20the%20Union%20on%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20the%20principle%20of%20separation%20of%20powers%20between%20the%20organs%20of%20government%20as%20well%20as%20between%20Union%20government%20and%20State%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhatia%E2%80%99s%20enunciation%20on%20the%20developments%20in%20judicial%20discourse%20of%20federalism%2C%20the%20workings%20of%20the%20anti-defection%20law%20and%20the%20role%20of%20Fourth%20Branch%20institutions%20are%20a%20crucial%20prism%20through%20which%20we%20should%20view%20these%20recent%20developments%20%E2%80%93%20and%20predict%20the%20manners%20in%20which%20this%20tension%20will%20continue%20to%20prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-483348%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGautam%20Bhatia%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20in%20August%202019.%20Image%3A%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Cem%3EUnsealed%20Covers%3C%2Fem%3E%20lies%20in%20Part%20III%20that%20is%2C%20judiciary.%20This%20section%20focuses%20on%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20an%20institution%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20the%20legacy%20of%20specific%20judges%20(as%20a%20keen%20observer%20may%20glean%20from%20the%20title%20of%20the%20book).%20This%20aspect%20of%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20work%20serves%20as%20a%20radical%20critique%20of%20an%20institution%20that%20though%20so%20central%20to%20the%20democratic%20structure%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20people%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20opaque%20in%20its%20functioning%20and%20often%20unwilling%20to%20accept%20rigorous%20public%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20highlights%20various%20instances%20where%20major%20questions%20were%20asked%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20court%2C%20and%20the%20responses%20were%20either%20found%20wanting%20or%20fundamentally%20contrary%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice.%20His%20articles%20on%20the%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20a%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20enquiry%20was%20conducted%2C%20and%20the%20questionable%20instances%20that%20played%20out%20are%20a%20stark%20indictment.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E..in%20effect%E2%80%A6.damned%20by%20five%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20men%20in%20the%20country%20before%20being%20heard%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20distressing%20legacy%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20that%2C%20the%20articles%20on%20the%20legacy%20of%20individual%20judges%20stand%20out%20as%20fascinating%20insights%20into%20the%20%E2%80%98polyvocal%E2%80%99%20nature%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20progress%20(or%20regress)%20of%20the%20jurisprudence%20of%20different%20strands%20of%20the%20law%20as%20influenced%20by%20specific%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Findia-supreme-court-people-centric-polyvocal-image%5C%22%3EIf%20Supreme%20Court%20Has%20to%20Remain%20People-Centric%2C%20It%20Has%20to%20Shed%20Its%20Polyvocal%20Image%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20obvious%20criticism%20is%20that%20Bhatia%20is%20not%20a%20detached%20observer%20as%20some%20may%20expect%20a%20chronicler%20of%20courts%20to%20be.%20He%20informs%20his%20reader%20of%20his%20involvement%20in%20a%20number%20of%20cases%20that%20he%20writes%20about.%20But%20Bhatia%2C%20unlike%20the%20law%2C%20makes%20no%20bones%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20decidedly%20not%20neutral%20or%20dispassionate.%20I%20would%20also%20further%20argue%20that%20this%20is%20in%20effect%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20work%20%E2%80%93%20that%20a%20lawyer%20and%20an%20academic%20who%20participated%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%20many%20of%20the%20cases%20he%20writes%20about%20offers%20a%20detailed%20perspective%20that%20the%20brightest%20of%20dispassionate%20and%20uninvolved%20observers%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20offer.%20This%20is%20best%20shown%20in%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Privacy%20(%3Cem%3EJustice%20K.S.%20Puttaswamy%20v.%20Union%20of%20India-%202017%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Section%20377%20(%3Cem%3ENavtej%20Johar%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20Aadhaar%20(%3Cem%3EJustice%20K.S.%20Puttaswamy%20v.%20Union%20of%20India-%202019%3C%2Fem%3E)%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20various%20instances%2C%20the%20efforts%20of%20Bhatia%20and%20other%20lawyers%20and%20journalists%20to%20critique%20the%20merits%20as%20well%20as%20the%20manner%20of%20functioning%20of%20individual%20cases%20and%20legal%20institutions%20have%20been%20questioned%20as%20contemptuous%20of%20the%20court.%20In%20fact%2C%20Bhatia%20himself%20deals%20with%20one%20such%20instance%20in%20his%20article%20regarding%20the%20curious%20workings%20of%20the%20many%20judges%20hearing%20the%20set%20of%20cases%20regarding%20interpretation%20of%20Section%2024%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act.%20In%20response%2C%20I%20submit%20that%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20court%20is%20more%20than%20capable%20of%20dealing%20with%20such%20criticism%20and%20is%20in%20fact%20strengthened%20by%20it.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20rigorous%20public%20debate%20about%20the%20merits%20of%20decision%20only%20strengthens%20belief%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20%E2%80%93%20a%20belief%20which%20is%20the%20very%20cornerstone%20on%20which%20rests%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20judiciary.%20Far%20from%20being%20discouraged%2C%20it%20should%20be%20promoted%20and%20celebrated.%20A%20world%20of%20law%20students%20engaging%20in%20debates%20on%20issues%20highlighted%20in%20this%20book%20can%20only%20serve%20as%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20the%20legal%20institutions%2C%20and%20society%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20preface%2C%20the%20author%20states%20that%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20demystify%2C%20democratise%2C%20and%20promote%20engagement%20with%20constitutional%20law.%20His%20work%2C%20in%20this%20book%20and%20beyond%2C%20has%20been%20hugely%20successful%20at%20doing%20so.%20I%20would%20take%20the%20liberty%20of%20adding%20a%20fourth%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20critical%20interrogation%20of%20the%20justice%20system%20of%20our%20nation.%20It%20is%20this%20that%20he%20has%20been%20successful%20at%20in%20challenging%20times%2C%20and%20for%20this%20his%20book%20deserves%20most%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArchit%20Krishna%20is%20a%20lawyer%20practicing%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694771271000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15151528%2Fhammer-620011_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-successful-critical-interrogation-of-indias-justice-system%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Bhatia's%20'Unsealed%20Covers'%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20parts%3A%20rights%2C%20constitutional%20structure%2C%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20each%20article%20covers%20a%20judgment%20(or%20a%20set%20of%20judgments)%20corresponding%20with%20the%20larger%20theme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-successful-critical-interrogation-of-indias-justice-system%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rubiales%20banned%20from%20going%20near%20player%20he%20kissed%20at%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694770560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F70x70%2Fskynews-jenni