in%20days%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98candid%20disclosure%E2%80%99%20of%20charges%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20among%20the%20many%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20released%2C%20and%20re-arrested%20several%20times%20over%20the%20past%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20struggle%20is%20part%20of%20a%20long%20battle%20for%20human%20rights%20and%20justice%20in%20a%20security%20paradigm%20under%20which%20enforced%20disappearances%2C%20encounter%20killings%2C%20media%20censorship%2C%20and%20police%20brutality%20have%20become%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20those%20who%20earlier%20condoned%20this%20security%20paradigm%20now%20find%20themselves%20facing%20the%20same%20heavy-handedness%20and%20lack%20of%20due%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20include%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-61055210%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremoved%20constitutionally%20by%20a%20vote%20of%20no-confidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202022%2C%20his%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%20members%20and%20supporters.%20The%20erstwhile%20opposition%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20formed%20a%20government%20for%20the%20remaining%2016%20months%20of%20the%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20five-tenure%2C%20which%20ended%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29164015%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-4.39.28-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29164015%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-4.39.28-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29164015%2FScreenshot-2023