20to%20expect%20better%20from%20a%20state%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20civil%20rights%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20said%20political%20analyst%20Azaz%20Syed%2C%20a%20senior%20journalist%20with%20Geo%20TV%20in%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20establishment%20%E2%80%9Cwanted%20an%20excuse%E2%80%9D%20to%20sideline%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20and%20they%20got%20it%2C%20he%20tells%20Sapan%20News.%20While%20violence%20is%20never%20acceptable%2C%20the%20violence%20committed%20by%20around%20a%20thousand%20individuals%20on%20May%209%20led%20to%20over%2010%2C000%20arrests%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20maintains%20that%20their%20protests%20were%20peaceful%20and%20that%20their%20members%20were%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-army-imran-khan-scorned%5C%22%3EHell%20Hath%20No%20Fury%20Like%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20Scorned%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrushing%20dissent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EDissenting%20voices%20in%20Balochistan%20province%20and%20the%20Federally%20Administered%20Tribal%20Areas%20(FATA)%20have%20long%20faced%20far%20worse.%20The%20number%20of%20missing%20persons%20in%20Balochistan%20alone%20has%20crossed%205%2C000%20since%20the%20early%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAli%20Wazir%2C%2046%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fpakistans-ali-wazir-the-lone-marxist-to-win-despite-taliban-killing-16-of-his-family%2F90002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Marxist%20activist%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20works%20in%20the%20transport%20business%2C%20is%20from%20North%20Waziristan%2C%20a%20tribal%20area%20bordering%20Afghanistan%20that%20has%20been%20a%20battleground%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20military%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20the%20Taliban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wazir%20family%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20to%20the%20Taliban%20has%20cost%20them%20dearly.%20The%20Taliban%20have%20killed%20several%20of%20their%20relatives.%20Five%2C%20including%20Ali%20Wazir%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20uncle%20and%20cousins%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20single%20ambush%20in%202005.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Wazir%20was%20a%20student%20at%20Gomal%20University%20in%20Dera%20Ismail%20Khan%2C%20imprisoned%20for%20a%20scuffle%20with%20a%20telephone%20operator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20February%202018%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20key%20leader%20of%20the%20civil-rights%20organisation%20Pashtun%20Tahaffuz%20(%E2%80%98protection%E2%80%99)%20Movement%2C%20which%20emerged%20from%20a%20student-led%20organisation%20started%20in%202014%20to%20protest%20the%20racial%20profiling%20of%20the%20Mehsud%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PTM%20holds%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20military%20responsible%20for%20cultivating%20the%20Taliban.%20News%20about%20them%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F877922%2Fin-pakistan-a-youth-led-social-media-powered-movement-is-gaining-ground-despite-a-media-blackout%5C%22%3Elargely%20censored%20in%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWazir%20survived%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20shortly%20before%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20last%20elections%20in%20July%202018%2C%20when%20he%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate.%20His%20participation%20in%20parliamentary%20sessions%20was%20impeded%20by%20sedition%20charges%20and%20imprisonment%20for%20over%20two%20years.%20He%20was%20finally%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1737111%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleased%20on%20bail%20in%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EArrests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20PTM%20rally%20of%2018%20August%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20in%20Tarnol%2C%20a%20Pashtun-dominated%20suburb%20of%20Islamabad.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%E2%80%9Cunknown%20persons%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fimaanzhazir%2Fstatus%2F1693025089518784718%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroke%20into%20Mazari-Hazir%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20home%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20where%20she%20lives%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20Shireen%20Mazari%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20core%20member%20of%20the%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHazir-Mazari%2C%2030%2C%20a%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20activist%20and%20human-rights%20defender%2C%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20PTI%20even%20when%20her%20mother%20was%20their%20human%20rights%20minister%20from%202019-2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShireen%20Mazari%20was%20arrested%20five%20times%20within%20a%20fortnight%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20She%20subsequently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1755265%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresigned%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20was%20in%20her%20night%20clothes%20and%20said%20%E2%80%98let%20me%20change%2C%E2%80%99%20but%20they%20just%20dragged%20her%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mazari%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fshireenmazari1%2Fstatus%2F1693037820053774833%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20also%20confiscated%20Imaan%E2%80%99s%20cellphone%20and%20laptop%2C%20plus%20the%20security%20cameras%2C%20showed%20no%20arrest%20warrant%2C%20and%20followed%20no%20legal%20procedures%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arrested%20activists%20were%20initially%20charged%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Penal%20Code%20and%20the%20Anti%20Terrorism%20Act%2C%20including%20the%20colonial-era%20%E2%80%98sedition%E2%80%99%20law%20that%20the%20Lahore%20High%20Court%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F3%2F30%2Fpakistani-court-strikes-down-sedition-law-in-win-for-free-speech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20as%20unconstitutional%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EExcellent%20news%20from%20Lahore%20High%20Court%20where%20the%20sedition%20law%20(section%20124-A)%20has%20been%20declared%20unconstitutional.%20This%20was%20a%20colonial%20law%20used%20to%20suppress%20dissent.%20I%20am%20personally%20faced%20sedition%20charges%20since%202019.%20Its%20a%20great%20moment%20for%20all%20who%20believe%20in%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ammar%20Ali%20Jan%20(%40ammaralijan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fammaralijan%2Fstatus%2F1641327345469386753%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20activists%20arrested%20after%20the%2018%20August%20rally%20secured%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geo.tv%2Flatest%2F507146-atc-approves-bail-applications-for-imaan-mazari-ali-wazir%5C%22%3Ebail%20in%20the%20sedition%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66637600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheld%20again%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20allegedly%20funding%20anti-state%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMazari-Hazir%20was%20granted%20bail%20on%202%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWazir%20and%20other%20PTM%20activists%20were%20granted%20bail%20on%20September%2011%20in%20the%20two%20remaining%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20but%20before%20they%20could%20walk%20out%20of%20jail%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fismatshahjahan%2Fstatus%2F1701257345928466546%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%3Ewere%20held%20again%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20unknown%20c