ity%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20military%20establishment%20manoeuvres%20the%20political%20game%20for%20their%20own%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jahangir.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20commit%20a%20crime%20%E2%80%9Cand%20then%20expect%20people%20not%20to%20criticise%20you%E2%80%9D%20and%20demand%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20the%20slogans%20should%20be%20according%20to%20your%20taste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20way%20out%20of%20this%20quagmire%20is%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20a%20democratic%20dispensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20the%20army%20should%20return%20to%20the%20barracks%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20not%20interfere%20in%20politics.%20Her%20words%20echo%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1349491%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estance%20consistently%20taken%20by%20her%20late%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20iconic%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20Asma%20Jahangir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-embed-handler%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20excerpt%20from%20BBC%20Urdu%20interview%20of%20late%20lawyer%20Asma%20Jahangir%20about%20the%20legitimacy%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20a%20caretaker%20setup%20governing%20Pakistan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20initially%20propped%20Khan%20up%20as%20one%20of%20those%20%E2%80%98projects%E2%80%99%2C%20those%20at%20the%20helm%20now%20seem%20determined%20to%20keep%20him%20away%20from%20the%20political%20process.%20They%20have%20also%20tried%20to%20manipulate%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(PPP)%20and%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(PML-N)%20but%20might%20not%20succeed%20as%20easily%20given%20these%20parties%E2%80%99%20longer%20track%20record%20in%20electoral%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhichever%20party%20or%20alliance%20comes%20to%20power%20after%20elections%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20within%20this%20year%2C%20the%20powers%20behind%20the%20scenes%20and%20the%20ongoing%20human%20rights%20violations%20are%20unlikely%20to%20change%20much%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAbdullah%20Zahid%20is%20an%20aspiring%20journalist%20studying%20mass%20communication%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Karachi.%20Follow%20him%20on%20X%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabdullahhzahid%3Fs%3D21%26t%3DYib5Dr6ZPTJCb9WElKcEJQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40AbdullahZahid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsapannews.com%5C%22%3ESapan%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20syndicated%20feature.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694767558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29164015%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-4.39.28-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-ongoing-arrests-and-the-future-of-pakistans-democracy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unpacking%20the%20context%20behind%20a%20cycle%20of%20arrests%2C%20bail%20and%20rearrests%20of%20activists%2C%20missing%20persons%2C%20and%20others%20in%20Pakistan%20who%20find%20themselves%20facing%20the%20lack%20of%20due%20process%20they%20had%20earlier%20condoned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-ongoing-arrests-and-the-future-of-pakistans-democracy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Policy%20Decision%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20SC%20Said%20While%20Upholding%20Removal%20of%20Meat%20from%20Lakshadweep's%20Midday%20Meals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arguing%20that%20the%20judiciary%20cannot%20%E2%80%9Cimport%20personal%20preferences%20in%20policy%20matters%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20upheld%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20to%20exclude%20meat%20from%20the%20Union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20mid-day%20meals%20and%20shut%20down%20its%20dairy%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20comprising%20Justices%20Aniruddha%20Bose%20and%20Bela%20Trivedi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.mathrubhumi.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fsc-upholds-omission-of-meat-products-in-midday-meals-in-lakshadweep-1.8903309%5C%22%3Ewas%20hearing%20a%20special%20leave%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20dismiss%20a%20plea%20against%20the%20Union%20territory%20administration%E2%80%99s%20decisions%2C%20which%20were%20taken%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20after%20BJP%20leader%20Praful%20Patel%20took%20charge%20as%20Lakshadweep%20administrator%20in%20late%202020%2C%20the%20Union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20administration%20removed%20meat%20products%20including%20chicken%20(but%20not%20fish)%20from%20its%20mid-day%20meal%20menu%20and%20shut%20down%20its%20state-run%20dairy%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2096%25%20of%20Lakshadweep%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20Muslim%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20150825155850%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.censusindia.gov.in%2F2011census%2FC-01%2FDDW00C-01%2520MDDS.XLS%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%202011%20census%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20Ajmal%20Ahmed%20R.%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flakshadweep-kerala-high-court-beef-ban-dairy-farm-midday-meal-praful-khoda-patel%5C%22%3Ehad%20argued%20in%20the%20high%20court%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20decision%20was%20designed%20to%20attack%20locals%E2%80%99%20food%20habits%20and%20said%20they%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20purchase%20dairy%20products%20imported%20from%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20closure%20of%20dairy%20farms%20would%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20sale%20and%20purchase%20of%20beef%20in%20the%20Union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20that%20year%2C%20the%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fdispatches%2Fkerala-high-court-stays-two-controversial-orders-of-lakshadweep-administration%2Farticle34927402.ece%5C%22%3Eimposed%20an%20interim%20stay%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20three%20months%20later%2C%20it%20dismissed%20a%20plea%20by%20Ahmed%20challenging%20the%20decision%2C%20accepting%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%20they%20were%20not%20obliged%20to%20provide%20non-vegetarian%20food%20in%20mid-day%20meals%20and%20that%20the%20islands%E2%80%99%20dairy%20farms%20were%20running%20at%20a%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20hesitation%20to%20hold%20that%20the%20petitioner%20has%20not%20made%20out%20any%20case%20of%20arbitrariness%20or%20illegality%20in%20the%20policy%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fkerala-high-court-upholds-lakshadweep-administration-policy-on-midday-meal-close-dairy-farm-182153%5C%22%3Eit%20said%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FD41DL4Eg_jM%3Fsi%3Dp9iDzmXSnoSf6lEz%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAhmed%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20following%20the%20dismissal%20of%20this%20plea.%20The%20top%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1023131%2Finclude-meat-in-midday-meals-supreme-court-tells-lakshadweep-administration-in-interim-order%5C%22%3Erevived%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20interim%20stay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lakshadweep%20administration%20had%20since%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20vacate%20this%20interim%20stay%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20exclusion%20of%20items%20from%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20menu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.mathrubhumi.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Flakshadweep-seeks-vacation-of-sc-s-interim-order-to-serve-chicken-meat-in-mid-day-meal-1.8845598%5C%22%3Ewas%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20remit%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it%20was%20a%20policy%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustices%20Bose%20and%20Trivedi%20concurred%20with%20this%20point%20of%20view%20on%20Thursday%20(September%2014).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20being%20questioned%20in%20this%20appeal%20is%20primarily%20a%20policy%20decision%20of%20the%20administration%20and%20no%20breach%20of%20any%20legal%20provision%20has%20been%20pointed%20out.%20It%20is%20not%20within%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20domain%20to%20decide%20as%20to%20what%20would%20be%20the%20choice%20of%20food%20for%20children%20of%20a%20particular%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-lakshadweep-mid-day-meal-237782%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20their%20order%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20will%20have%20to%20accept%20the%20administrative%20decision%20unless%20some%20outstanding%20arbitrariness%20is%20pointed%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20I.H.%20Syed%2C%20said%20during%20the%20hearing%20that%20the%20new%20food%20items%20%E2%80%93%20among%20which%20are%20fruits%20and%20dry%20fruits%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20culturally%20acceptable%20to%20Lakshadweep%E2%80%99s%20people%2C%20Justice%20Trivedi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsupreme-court-upholds-lakshadweep-decision-remove-meat-mid-day-meals-schools-dairy-farms%5C%22%3Easked%20if%20%E2%80%9Cdry%20fruits%20%5Bwere%20not%20liked%5D%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bose%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20after%20passing%20the%20order%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20cannot%20import%20personal%20preferences%20in%20policy%20matters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lakshadweep%20administration%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20have%20been%20criticised%20for%20not%20involving%20enough%20consultation%20with%20the%20islands%E2%80%99%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmesh%20Saigal%2C%20a%20former%20administrator%20of%20the%20island%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20while%20a%20ban%20on%20bovine%20slaughter%20was%20understandable%2C%20the%20attempt%20to%20ban%20beef%20products%20in%20Lakshadweep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwatch-anti-muslim-prejudice-behind-new-policies-former-lakshadweep-administrator%5C%22%3Ereflected%20anti-Muslim%20prejudice%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20sharply%20criticised%20the%20administrator%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20permit%20consumption%20of%20alcohol%20in%20what%20are%20called%20inhabited%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694766131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsupreme-court-upholds-exclusion-of-meat-from-lakshadweep-midday-meals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20said%20it%20was%20not%20within%20the%20court's%20remit%20to%20decide%20the%20choice%20of%20food%20for%20the%20children%20of%20a%20particular%20region%2C%20leaving%20it%20to%20the%20government%20to%20decide%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsupreme-court-upholds-exclusion-of-meat-from-lakshadweep-midday-meals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Jawan%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20Makes%20Asking%20Serious%20Questions%20Look%20Sexy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15130125%2FJawan.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENiccolo%20Machiavelli%2C%20had%20he%20seen%20the%20new%20Indian%20blockbuster%20%3Cem%3EJawan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Soldier)%20taking%20the%20world%20by%20storm%2C%20would%20be%20delighted%20that%20his%20key%20idea%20%E2%80%93%20of%20active%20citizenship%20in%20a%20republic%20%E2%80%93%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20it.%20Machiavelli%2C%20admirer%20of%20Greeks%20and%20Romans%2C%20was%20convinced%20that%20citizens%20need%20to%20remain%20continually%20active%20and%20vigilant%20between%20the%20times%20they%20vote.%20Without%20this%20alertness%20and%20engagement%20in%20civic%20matters%2C%20there%20could%20be%20no%20enduring%20republic%2C%20and%20without%20such%20republican%20values%20there%20could%20be%20no%20true%20democracy.%20The%20American%20founding%20fathers%20took%20that%20lesson%20to%20heart%20well%2C%20as%20did%20the%20Indians%20when%20they%20named%20India%20a%20Democratic%20Republic.%20And%20in%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20movie%20star%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20(SRK)%20charismatically%20conveys%20this%20simple%20but%20powerful%20political%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpressinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fjawan-smashes-records-rakes-in-500-crore-worldwide-in-just-4-days%2F%5C%22%3Egrossed%20%2460%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20first%20four%20days%20alone%2C%20the%20film%20presents%20Khan%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20his%20multiple%20avatars%20as%20the%20ultimate%20avenger%20of%20justice%2C%20humiliating%20ill-informed%20ministers%2C%20exposing%20corrupt%20and%20inefficient%20governments%20and%20crony%20capitalists%2C%20redistributing%20money%20to%20the%20most%20vulnerable%2C%20discussing%20agrarian%20distress%20and%20getting%20justice%20for%20those%20punished%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth.%20He%20does%20all%20this%20with%20SRK%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20charm%20and%20athleticism%2C%20becoming%20a%20hero%20of%20the%20masses%20in%20the%20film%20and%20in%20the%20theatres.%20He%20educates%20people%20about%20the%20stark%20inequalities%20that%20they%20choose%20not%20to%20notice%2C%20while%20thrilling%20them%20by%20outwitting%20the%20baddies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20the%20Fine%20Art%20of%20Managing%20Contradictions%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fshah-rukh-khan-and-the-fine-art-of-managing-contradictions%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20the%20Fine%20Art%20of%20Managing%20Contradictions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20stylistic%20mash-up%20cinematically%20with%20over%20the%20top%20action%20sequences%2C%20romantic%20ballads%20and%20multiple%20roles%20for%20the%20hero.%20But%20that%20is%20to%20miss%20its%20real%20draw%2C%20which%20is%20the%20link%20to%20SRK%E2%80%99s%20own%20recent%20life.%20King%20Khan%20to%20his%20enormous%20fan%20base%2C%20he%20is%20the%20only%20star%20whose%20off-screen%20persona%20is%20as%20admired%20as%20the%20heroes%20he%20plays.%20But%20he%20is%20Muslim%20and%20lives%20in%20India%20where%20the%20dominant%20ideology%20of%20the%20Modi-led%20government%20is%20%E2%80%98Hindutva%E2%80%99%20or%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%2C%20in%20a%20flagrant%20disregard%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20commitment%20to%20religious%20diversity.%20Some%20years%20ago%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-34707247%5C%22%3Emildly%20critical%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20new%20vulnerability%20of%20religious%20minorities%20in%20India%20and%20for%20that%20he%20faced%20a%20virulent%20attack%20by%20right-wing%20trolls%20and%20his%20films%20faced%20boycott.%20He%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20made%20a%20political%20statement%20since%2C%20to%20the%20frustration%20of%20those%20who%20want%20all%20those%20in%20the%20public%20eye%20to%20take%20a%20stand.%20But%20despite%20his%20restraint%2C%20two%20years%20ago%20a%20government%20agency%20jailed%20his%20son%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fncb-drops-drugs-case-against-aryan-khan-five-others-says-lack-of-sufficient-evidence%5C%22%3Ewithout%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20drugs%20they%20said%20he%20had%20carried.%20SRK%20is%20a%20doting%20father%20and%20talks%20of%20his%20children%20often.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20the%20government%20decided%20that%20punishing%20the%20most%20famous%20Indian%20Muslim%20by%20hitting%20him%20where%20it%20would%20hurt%20most%20would%20demonstrate%20their%20supremacy%20nicely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20400px)%2085vw%2C%20400px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F03150919%2F86722463.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F03150919%2F86722463.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F03150919%2F86722463-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-555735%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Aryan%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESRK%20and%20his%20wife%20maintained%20a%20dignified%20silence%20through%20the%20ordeal%20but%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20outpouring%20of%20sympathy%20for%20them.%20Social%20media%20was%20flooded%20with%20anecdotes%20of%20his%20endless%20acts%20of%20kindness%20and%20plain%20decency%20over%20the%20years%20to%20technicians%2C%20junior%20journalists%2C%20younger%20colleagues%20and%20ordinary%20people.%20Women%20noted%20his%20impeccable%20chivalry%20even%20when%20no%20one%20was%20looking.%20Everyone%20praised%20his%20ready%20wit%20and%20intelligence.%20All%20agreed%20the%20arrest%20of%20his%20son%20was%20politically%20motivated.%20His%20lawyers%20did%20manage%20to%20have%20the%20young%20man%20released%20and%20the%20charges%20were%20dropped%20this%20year%20because%20of%20the%20complete%20lack%20of%20evidence.%20In%20response%2C%20rather%20than%20make%20a%20statement%20and%20again%20jeopardise%20a%20film%20that%20supports%20thousands%20of%20livelihoods%2C%20SRK%20did%20what%20he%20does%20best%20and%20%3Cem%3EJawan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20the%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinutes%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20film%2C%20before%20the%20audience%20walks%20away%20and%20their%20suspension%20of%20disbelief%20ends%2C%20SRK%20appears%20on%20the%20screen%20alone%20and%20talks%20directly%20to%20camera.%20Holding%20each%20viewer%20in%20his%20gaze%2C%20he%20chastises%20us%20for%20asking%20more%20questions%20about%20whether%20a%20laundry%20powder%20works%20than%20of%20the%20governments%20we%20elect.%20He%20reminds%20and%20admonishes%20the%20audience%20that%20they%2C%20the%20ordinary%20citizens%2C%20need%20to%20recognise%20they%20are%20the%20real%20superheroes%2C%20for%20they%20live%20in%20democracies%20and%20possess%20the%20vote%20which%20is%20their%20ultimate%20superpower.%20%E2%80%98Choose%20wisely%E2%80%99%20he%20tells%20them%20%E2%80%93%20and%20once%20you%20have%2C%20keep%20asking%20questions.%20His%20unmistakable%20political%20message%2C%20like%20Machiavelli%2C%20is%20that%20democracy%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20left%20to%20politicians%20without%20the%20constant%20vigilance%20of%20%E2%80%98active%20citizens%E2%80%99.%20The%20film%20is%20Indian%2C%20but%20this%20message%20is%20true%20for%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22SRK%2C%20I%20Hear%20You.%20And%20So%20Does%20Everyone%20Else.%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fsrk-i-hear-you-and-so-does-everyone-else%5C%22%3ESRK%2C%20I%20Hear%20You.%20And%20So%20Does%20Everyone%20Else.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMessage%20delivered%2C%20he%20goes%20back%20to%20one%20last%20breath-taking%20stunt%20in%20this%20high%20octane%20hugely%20fun%20film.%20The%20reaction%20to%20the%20film%20has%20been%20bonkers.%20SRK%20Fan%20Clubs%20have%20organised%20huge%20banners%20and%20celebrations%20in%20cinema%20halls%20across%20India%20and%20abroad.%20Audiences%20comes%20to%20watch%20the%20film%20with%20their%20faces%20wrapped%20in%20bandages%20and%20masks%20%E2%80%93%20the%20hero%E2%80%99s%20signature%20look.%20Shah%20Rukhs%E2%80%99s%20famous%20dance%20moves%20have%20been%20memorised%20and%20are%20performed%20wearing%20red%20shirts%20just%20like%20him%20and%20%E2%80%98with%20him%E2%80%99%20during%20screenings.%20People%20are%20going%20back%20to%20watch%20it%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20this%20hysteria%3F%20It%20is%20SRK%E2%80%99s%20huge%20draw%20of%20course%2C%20but%20also%20that%20people%20want%20to%20be%20told%2C%20by%20him%2C%20that%20they%20too%20can%20be%20heroic%20and%20vanquish%20the%20powerful%20by%20being%20active%20citizens%20and%20thinking%20hard%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20country%20they%20want%20to%20live%20in.%20Most%20of%20all%2C%20he%20communicates%20the%20truth%20about%20democratic%20politics%20and%20civic%20virtue%20in%20the%20language%20of%20emotion.%20Progressive%20politics%20too%20needs%20an%20emotional%20tug%2C%20something%20right-wing%20politics%20is%20adept%20at%20manufacturing%2C%20but%20which%20has%20been%20lacking%20on%20the%20centre-left%20in%20India%20and%20elsewhere.%20SRK%20shows%20a%20different%20way%20by%20confidently%20harnessing%20the%20love%20millions%20feel%20for%20him%20to%20make%20serious%20points%2C%20making%20his%20audiences%20feel%20good%20about%20themselves%20in%20the%20process%2C%20making%20the%20posing%20of%20difficult%20questions%20look%20sexy%20and%20charming%2C%20just%20like%20him.%20As%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshowed%2C%20even%20lessons%20in%20feminism%2