t%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20able%20to%20procure%20a%20borewell%2C%20purified%20water%20plant%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20built%20a%20beautiful%20library%20with%201000%20books%2C%20through%20their%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRajendra%20has%20helped%20tremendously%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20school.%20He%20is%20the%20person%20through%20whom%20we%20got%20most%20of%20the%20donations.%20The%20Washington%20Telangana%20Association%20(WATA)%20helped%20us%20get%2040%20benches%20for%20the%20school%20because%20of%20his%20efforts.%20A%20local%20MLA%20installed%20the%20borewell%20and%20an%20RO%20plant%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20learning%20more%20fun%2C%20through%20digital%20technology%20and%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20(ICT)%20initiative%2C%20she%20procured%20five%20computers%2C%20two%20LED%20projectors%20and%20two%20additional%20classrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICT%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20School%20Scheme%20was%20launched%20in%20December%202004%20to%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20secondary%20stage%20students%20to%20mainly%20build%20their%20capacity%20on%20ICT%20skills%20and%20make%20them%20learn%20through%20the%20computer-aided%20learning%20process.%20She%20proudly%20states%20that%20her%20students%20are%20now%20able%20to%20use%20computers%20proficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20living%20in%20an%20era%20of%20globalisation.%20To%20be%20a%20global%20citizen%2C%20digital%20education%20is%20a%20must.%20I%20want%20my%20students%20to%20know%20how%20to%20operate%20computers%20well%20and%20therefore%2C%20am%20exposing%20them%20to%20the%20technology%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20headmistress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20holistic%20education%20a%20must%20for%20this%20school%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESmt.%20Archana%20Nooguri%2C%20a%20National%20Awardee%20Teacher%202023%20from%20Telangana%2C%20works%20on%20improving%20enrolment%20rates%20%26amp%3B%20reducing%20dropouts.%20She%20develops%20low-cost%20teaching-learning%20material.%20She%20involved%20the%20community%20in%20setting%20up%20water%20purification%20plant%2C%20library%20etc.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FOurTeachersOurPrerna%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23OurTeachersOurPrerna%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeU7InH6xFN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FeU7InH6xFN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20(%40EduMinOfIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEduMinOfIndia%2Fstatus%2F1699030560587608210%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%20100%20girl%20students%2C%20Archana%20wanted%20them%20to%20learn%20self-defence.%20She%20arranged%20for%20karate%20classes%20twice%20a%20week%20through%20a%20private%20instructor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20having%20bookish%20knowledge%20is%20not%20enough.%20I%20want%20the%20students%20to%20excel%20in%20all%20aspects%20of%20life.%20Sports%20should%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20student%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20I%20arranged%20for%20a%20karate%20and%20dance%20class%20for%20students.%20The%20students%20have%20excelled%20in%20karate%20competitions%20at%20both%20state%20and%20national%20levels%20and%20one%20student%20even%20secured%20admission%20at%20a%20sports%20school%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20parents%E2%80%99%20request%2C%20Archana%20also%20introduced%20English%20as%20the%20medium%20of%20education%20at%20the%20school%20in%202016.%20She%20says%20that%20this%20is%20the%20first%20English%20medium%20government%20primary%20school%20in%20their%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%