n%3Cp%3EBut%20what%E2%80%99s%20even%20more%20awe-inspiring%20is%20that%20Renu%20is%2058%20years%20old.%20When%20people%20ask%20her%20what%20keeps%20her%20going%20at%20this%20age%2C%20she%20merely%20responds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20once%2C%20I%20am%20doing%20something%20for%20myself%20and%20not%20for%20anyone%20else.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Renu%20started%20her%20cycling%20journey%20in%202017%2C%20she%20has%20inspired%20countless%20Indian%20women%20wary%20of%20cycling%20to%20take%20to%20the%20streets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20woman%20was%20Gareema%20Shankar%20(44)%20from%20Delhi.%20Though%20Gareema%20had%20also%20been%20cycling%20since%202017%2C%20she%20recalls%20how%20she%20would%20only%20do%20it%20at%20the%20park%20near%20her%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20stay%20hidden%20from%20my%20parents%20and%20only%20cycle%20once%20I%20dropped%20my%20son%20off%20at%20school.%20I%20had%20never%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312521%2Fcyclist-chanchal-kunwar-singh-cycles-across-india-to-spread-climate-change-awareness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecycled%20on%20the%20roads%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Delhi%20because%20I%20did%20not%20want%20people%20I%20knew%20to%20see%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20adds%20that%202021%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20her.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20to%20know%20about%20Renuji%E2%80%99s%20story%20on%20a%20Zoom%20call%20that%20was%20being%20hosted%20by%20an%20organisation.%20When%20I%20figured%20the%20age%20at%20which%20she%20had%20started%20cycling%2C%20I%20asked%20myself%20%E2%80%98What%E2%80%99s%20stopping%20you%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGareema%20adds%20that%20being%20a%20mother%20to%20an%208-year-old%20and%20juggling%20work%20and%20home%20brought%20its%20own%20set%20of%20doubts.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20I%20would%20follow%20Renuji%E2%80%99s%20acc