-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%202.5%20acre%20land%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jyoti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20still%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20I%20was%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20Textile%20Gallery%20at%20the%20City%20Palace.%20But%20we%20both%20had%20a%20nagging%20thought%20that%20our%20lives%20were%20not%20being%20used%20creatively.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20after%2013%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20my%20husband%20left%20the%20service%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20developing%20this%20land%20we%20had%20bought%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Devra%E2%80%99%2C%20by%20which%20they%20christened%20this%20plot%2C%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20local%20name%20given%20to%20tribal%20temples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Army%2C%20Major%20says%20his%20guiding%20belief%20has%20always%20centred%20around%20serving%20both%20the%20nation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300372%2F8-pocket-friendly-cosy-homestays-in-the-mountains-for-that-scenic-winter-break%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20this%20(Devra)%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20cultivate%20a%20generation%20that%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20their%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20making%20the%20dream%20come%20true%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202229px)%20100vw%2C%202229px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Devra%20the%20local%20women%20of%20Udaipur%20get%