mestay-banyan-bliss-ethnic-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Udaipur%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20being%20silenced.%20%E2%80%9CIn%201999%2C%20I%20decided%20there%20was%20no%20better%20time%20than%20the%20present%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20land%20and%20this%20time%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20plan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202004%2C%20when%20Devra%20officially%20started%20welcoming%20guests%2C%20Jyoti%20would%20make%20frequent%20trips%20between%20Delhi%2C%20where%20her%20husband%20and%20child%20were%2C%20and%20Udaipur%2C%20where%20her%20dream%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20years%20were%20beautiful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20journey%20of%20inking%20relationships%20with%20the%20craftsmen%20of%20the%20city%2C%20since%20architects%20and%20civil%20engineers%20were%20tough%20to%20find%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20got%20a%20local%20person%2C%20Shivji%2C%20on%20board%2C%20and%20he%20helped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20the%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20what%20it%20is%20today.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Shivji%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Rupa%20%3Cem%3EBai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(an%20honorific%20to%20describe%20a%20woman)%2C%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20staff%20at%20Devra.%20She%20has%20witnessed%20the%20evolution%20of%20both%20the%20homestay%2C%20and%20the%20city%2C%20through%20these%20years%20and%20calls%20it%20a%20privilege.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20progress%20of%20our%20family%2C%20and%20of%20Devra%2C%20is%20inseparable.%20We%20have%20watched%20our%20children%20grow%20alongside%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20memories%20of%20their%20early%20years%20are%20woven%20into%20every%20brick%20and%20corner%20that%20my%20husband%20assembled%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rupa%20Bai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20Jyoti%20has%20enjoyed%20Rupa%20Bai%E2%80%99s%20company%20among%20the%20many%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeautiful%20connections%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20cemented.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20taught%20me%20to%20be%20patient%20and%20take%20things%20as%20they%20come.%20Everything%20happens%20in%20its%20own%20space%20and%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202229px)%20100vw%2C%202229px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devra%20prides%20itself%20on%20traditional%20Udaipur%20culture%20and%20authentic%20delicacies%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819.jpg%202229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%2