ade%20with%20watermelon%20crust)%2C%20%3Cem%3Emint%20lauki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bottle%20gourd%20and%20mint%20juice)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(corn)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20chulha%20rotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20with%20love%20by%20Rupa%20Bai%2C%20every%20dish%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearthy%20notes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%20is%20that%20you%20could%20learn%20to%20cook%20this%20feast%20yourself%20at%20the%20Heritage%20Cooking%20Class%20hosted%20by%20Jyoti.%20Credit%20her%20for%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98masterchef%E2%80%99%20and%20she%20brushes%20it%20off%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20farming%20techniques%20and%20fertilisers%20used%20on%20the%20land%20are%20the%20real%20heroes%20of%20this%20cooking.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20permaculture%20method%20followed%20at%20Devra%20ensures%20crop%20diversity%2C%20while%20improving%20soil%20fertility%20and%20increasing%20water%20conservation.%20Add%20to%20that%20Jyoti%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98secret%E2%80%99%20homemade%20fertilisers%20%E2%80%94%20onion%20peels%20in%20water%20and%20eggshells%20with%20bananas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286607%2Ffriends-quit-job-to-build-ecofriendly-home-stay-for-weekend-getaway-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20produce%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3Etastes%20so%20wonderful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fe8f21314fbfb40e8b1a2e17942971cce-1694171998.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rooms%20at%20Devra%20have%20been%20done%20up%2