%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1-1694173056.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1-1694173056-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1-1694173056-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1-1694173056-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1-1694173056-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20allows%20users%20to%20scan%20the%20QR%20code%20on%20its%20water%20cans%20and%20get%20details%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20cans.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undp.org%2Fkosovo%2Fblog%2Fmicroplastics-human-health-how-much-do-they-harm-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNDP%20article%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereveals%20that%20microplastics%20have%20been%20found%20in%20tap%20water%2C%20as%20well%20as%20bottled%20water.%20These%20compounds%20are%20linked%20to%20serious%20health%20issues%20such%20as%20endocrine%20disruption%2C%20weight%20gain%2C%20insulin%20resistance%2C%20decreased%20reproductive%20health%2C%20cancer%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20is%20scary.%20Based%20on%20our%20research%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20these%20cans%20should%20be%20disposed%20of%20after%2040%20times%20of%20use.%20Post%20that%2C%20they%20start%20losing%20their%20structural%20integrity.%20But%20the%20problem%20is%2C%20how%20to%20determine%20the%20number%20of%20times%20the%20can%20has%20been%20used%3F%20There%20is%20no%20tracking%2C%20there%20is%20no%20marker%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bharath%20(43)%20points%20out%20that%20people%20have%20come%20to%20accept%20these%20dirty%20cans%20as%20is.%20Nobody%20really%20questions%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20drink%20Ganga%20river%E2%80%99s%20water%20from%20a%20bathroom%20bucket%3F%20No.%20Likewise%2C%20we%20have%20accepted%20that%20these%20dirty%20plastic%20water%20cans%20are%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20wanted%20to%20use%20IoT%20tech%20to%20solve%20these%20problems%20and%20that%20is%20when%20their%20%E2%80%9Cconnected%20cans%E2%80%9D%20concept%20was%20born.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20siblings%20launched%20BookWater%20and%20were%20joined%20by%20Sameer%20and%20Hariharan%20about%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20the%20QR%20do%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20brothers%20manufacture%20ISI%20(Indian%20Standards%20Institution)-rated%20plastic%20cans%20where%20they%20stick%20a%20QR%20code%20on%20every%20can.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20IoT%20sensors%20in%20the%20copackers%E2%80%99%20locations.%20Our%20sensors%20monitor%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20and%20where%20it%20is%20filled.%20If%20you%20order%20a%20can%20through%20the%20BookWater%20app%2C%20you%20can%20scan%20the%20QR%20code%20and%20quality%20reports%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20the%20cans%20are%20left%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20UV%20rays%20break%20the%20plastic%20particles%20and%20shed%20copious%20amounts%20of%20microplastics%20into%20the%20water.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-3-1694173807-300x157.jpg%20